r%20the%20dreams%20of%20those%20struggling%20for%20social%20justice.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThis%20is%20BJP's%20character%20and%20the%20difference%20between%20symbolic%20justice%20and%20real%20justice.%20The%20Congress%20will%20never%20let%20this%20happen.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20fight%20for%20social%20justice%20and%20will%20ensure%20that%20eligible%20candidates%20fill%20up%20these%20vacant%20positions%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20draft%20guidelines%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Breserved%20vacancy%20may%20be%20declared%20unreserved%20by%20following%20the%20procedure%20of%20de-reservation%20where%20after%2C%20it%20can%20be%20filled%20as%20an%20unreserved%20vacancy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20general%20ban%20on%20de-reservation%20of%20reserved%20vacancies%20in%20case%20of%20direct%20recruitment.%20However%2C%20in%20rare%20and%20exceptional%20cases%20when%20a%20vacancy%20in%20a%20Group%20A%20service%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20to%20remain%20vacant%20in%20public%20interest%2C%20the%20University%20concerned%20may%20prepare%20a%20proposal%20for%20de-reservation%20of%20the%20vacancy%20giving%20the%20following%20information%3A%20'The%20proposal%20will%20be%20required%20to%20list%20-%20efforts%20made%20to%20fill%20up%20the%20post%3B%20reasons%20why%20it%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20to%20remain%20vacant%20and%20justification%20for%20de-reservation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20draft%20guidelines%20stated%2C%20detailing%20the%20process%20for%20filling%20up%20such%20a%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20draft%20guidelines%20sparked%20a%20huge%20row%2C%20drawing%20strong%20criticism%20from%20the%20main%20Opposition%20Congress.%20Earlier%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20had%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20end%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20outcry%2C%20Union%20Education%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20assured%20that%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20single%20reserved%20post%20will%20be%20de-reserved%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20scope%20for%20ambiguity%20after%20the%20Central%20Educational%20Institutions%20(Reservation%20in%20Teachers'%20Cadre)%20Act%2C%202019%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UGC%2C%20too%2C%20came%20out%20with%20a%20clarification.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20to%20clarify%20that%20there%20has%20been%20no%20de-reservation%20of%20reserved%20category%20positions%20in%20Central%20Educational%20Institutions%20(CEI)%20in%20the%20past%20and%20there%20is%20going%20to%20be%20no%20such%20de-reservation.%20It%20is%20important%20for%20all%20HEIs%20(higher%20education%20institutions)%20to%20ensure%20that%20all%20backlog%20positions%20in%20reserved%20category%20are%20filled%20up%20through%20concerted%20efforts%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20quoting%20UGC%20chairman%20M%20Jagadesh%20Kumar%20was%20posted%20by%20the%20panel's%20official%20handle%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706526240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fomeiiiko_rahul-gandhi-pti-_625x300_22_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Freservation-ugc-rahul-gandhi-rahul-gandhis-post-after-outcry-over-education-panel-ugcs-draft-rules-4953699%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20alleged%20a%20conspiracy%20by%20RSS-BJP%20to%20do%20away%20with%20caste-based%20reservation%20in%20higher%20education%20and%20said%20the%20Congress%20%26quot%3Bwill%20never%20let%20this%20happen%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Freservation-ugc-rahul-gandhi-rahul-gandhis-post-after-outcry-over-education-panel-ugcs-draft-rules-4953699%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Freservation-ugc-rahul-gandhi-rahul-gandhis-post-after-outcry-over-education-panel-ugcs-draft-rules-4953699%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampU