%20stranger%20helped%20his%20mother-in-law%20with%20Alzheimer's%20disease.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20X%20user%20named%20Dave%20in%20a%20long%20post%20shared%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20wife's%20mom%20has%20Alzheimer's%20disease.%20Earlier%20tonight%2C%20we%20left%20her%20parents%20alone%20at%20their%20Airbnb%20while%20we%20took%20the%20kids%20to%20urgent%20care%20for%20ear%20infections.%20Her%20dad%20fell%20asleep%20on%20the%20couch.%20Her%20mom%20wandered%20out%20the%20door...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20rushed%20back%20as%20soon%20as%20we%20heard%20she%20was%20missing.%20It%20was%20dark%20and%20raining%20steadily.%20Her%20coat%20was%20still%20on%20the%20rack.%20Her%20wallet%20still%20on%20the%20table.%20I%20ran%20up%20and%20down%20the%20block%20asking%20neighbors%20if%20they%20had%20seen%20her.%20We%20got%20in%20our%20cars%20and%20combed%20the%20entire%20neighborhood.%20No%20luck.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20decided%20to%20check%20out%20a%20shopping%20center%20a%20few%20blocks%20away%20hoping%20that%20she%20had%20been%20drawn%20to%20the%20bright%20lights.%20I%20drove%20by%20the%20front%20entrance%20of%20the%20grocery%20store%20and%2C%20amazingly%2C%20saw%20her%20through%20the%20window%20sitting%20at%20a%20table%20in%20the%20coffee%20shop%20with%20a%20woman%20I%20didn't%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20parked%20and%20ran%20into%20the%20store.%20I%20found%20them%20sipping%20tea%20and%20talking%20cheerfully.%20I%20told%20the%20woman%20who%20I%20was%20and%20thanked%20her%20for%20watching%20after%20my%20mother-in-law.%20The%20woman%20and%20her%20partner%20had%20noticed%20her%20in%20the%20parking%20lot%20looking%20confused%2C%20so%20they%20had%20guided%20her%20into%20the%20store%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDave%20mentioned%20that%20the%20stranger%20helped%20his%20mom-in-law%20shop%20for%20bread%20and%20cookies%20and%20then%20paid%20for%20them%20since%20she%20had%20no%20money%20or%20credit%20cards.%20%26quot%3BThey%20sat%20with%20her%20while%20the%20store%20employees%20scrambled%20to%20locate%20her%20caretaker.%20They%20were%20exactly%20the%20people%20you%20would%20hope%20to%20find%20in%20this%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20tweet%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDave%20further%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20thanked%20them%20for%20treating%20her%20with%20such%20warmth%20and%20dignity.%20They%20wouldn't%20let%20me%20pay%20them%20back%20for%20the%20groceries%20or%20tea.%20We%20don't%20know%20their%20names%20or%20anything%20else%20about%20them%2C%20but%20we%20will%20always%20be%20thankful%20that%20they%20identified%20our%20problem%20and%20stopped%20to%20help.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20concluded%20his%20post%20by%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20good%20people%20left%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20our%20family%20is%20eternally%20grateful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMy%20wife's%20mom%20has%20Alzheimer's%20disease.%20Earlier%20tonight%2C%20we%20left%20her%20parents%20alone%20at%20their%20Airbnb%20while%20we%20took%20the%20kids%20to%20urgent%20care%20for%20ear%20infections.%20Her%20dad%20fell%20asleep%20on%20the%20couch.%20Her%20mom%20wandered%20out%20the%20door%E2%80%A6%20%F0%9F%A7%B5%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20dave%20(%40davethompsonMD)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FdavethompsonMD%2Fstatus%2F1751461110430183577%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2028%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20the%20post%20has%20amassed%206.8%20million%20views%20and%2061%2C000%20likes%20and%206%2C400%20retweets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heartwarming%20post%20is%20winning%20hearts%20on%20the%20internet.%20A%20user%20commented%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20so%20