ck_625x300_29_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fghaziabad-news%2Fdog-attack-on-camera-pack-of-stray-dogs-attack-child-in-ghaziabad-apartment-4953021%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20yet%20another%20incident%20of%20the%20dog%20menace%2C%20a%20pack%20of%20stray%20dogs%20attacked%20a%20child%20in%20an%20apartment%20in%20Ghaziabad%20while%20he%20was%20playing%20putside%20in%20the%20compound%20area.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fghaziabad-news%2Fdog-attack-on-camera-pack-of-stray-dogs-attack-child-in-ghaziabad-apartment-4953021%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fghaziabad-news%2Fdog-attack-on-camera-pack-of-stray-dogs-attack-child-in-ghaziabad-apartment-4953021%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fghaziabad-news%2Fdog-attack-on-camera-pack-of-stray-dogs-attack-child-in-ghaziabad-apartment-4953021%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20End%20Of%20The%20Road%20For%20The%20I.N.D.I.A%20Grouping%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20coalition%20was%20announced%20in%20July%202023%2C%20it%20raised%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20hope.%20Just%20two%20months%20before%2C%20in%20May%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20pulled%20off%20a%20stunning%20victory%20against%20the%20BJP%20in%20Karnataka.%20The%20results%20clearly%20demonstrated%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20its%20weaknesses.%20If%20the%20opposition%20parties%20played%20their%20cards%20right%2C%20the%20BJP%20could%20be%20challenged.%20It%20was%20against%20this%20backdrop%20of%20hope%20that%20the%20grand%20coalition%20of%20opposition%20parties%20was%20launched.%20However%2C%20with%20just%20three%20months%20to%20the%20election%2C%20the%20alliance%20appears%20to%20be%20collapsing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%2C%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20opposition%20alliance%2C%20has%20reunited%20with%20the%20BJP%20-%20again%20-%20in%20Bihar%2C%20turning%20his%20back%20on%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20bloc%20and%20his%20ambition%20to%20defeat%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20the%20coming%20election.%20The%20man%20of%20multiple%20u-turns%20has%20dealt%20a%20body%20blow%20to%20the%20hopes%20of%20the%20opposition%2C%20especially%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2024%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20fired%20the%20first%20shot%20by%20stating%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20would%20fight%20the%20election%20alone%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20This%20was%20soon%20followed%20by%20the%20AAP%2C%20which%20announced%20a%20solo%20fight%20in%20Punjab.%20The%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20and%20AAP%20announcements%20do%20not%20come%20as%20a%20surprise.%20The%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20grouping%20has%20multiple%20ideological%20and%20political%20contradictions%2C%20which%20were%20bound%20to%20surface%20at%20some%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20underpinning%20logic%20of%20forming%20the%20alliance%20was%20simple.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20got%20a%20pan-India%20vote%20share%20of%2037.3%25.%20The%20non-BJP%20vote%20across%20India%20account%20for%20just%20below%2063%25.%20If%20this%2063%25%20went%20to%20just%20one%20opposition%20party%2C%20the%20BJP%20could%20be%20stopped.%20The%20BJP%20was%20winning%20because%20the%20opposition%20vote%20was%20divided.%20Arithmetically%2C%20there%20is%20sense%20in%20this%20argument.%20It%20is%20a%20simple%20case%20of%20ensuring%20the%20non-BJP%20vote%20comes%20to%20just%20one%20single%20party.%20While%20there%20is%20simple%20math%20behind%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20grouping%2C%20the%20electoral%20realities%20are%20not%20so%20simple.%20There%20are%20two%20challenges%20that%20neutralize%20the%20arithmetic.%20First%2C%20there%20is%20a%20fundamental%20difference%20between%20arithmetic%20and%20chemistry.%20Pre-poll%20coalitions%20are%20not%20formed%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20arithmetic%20convenience%20but%20rather%20on%20chemistry%20and%20ideological%20compatibility.%20Secondly%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20there%20are%20important%20ideological%20and%20political%20contradictions%20between%20the%20numerous%20parties%20within%20the%20alliance.%20The%20Trinamool%20and%20AAP's%20decision%20to%20contest%20alone%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20these%20fundamental%20contradictions%20coming%20to%20the%20surface.%20I%20will%20discuss%20both%20these%20points%20in%20further%20detail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20pre-poll%20alliances%20like%20I.N.D.I.A%20are%20formed%2C%20the%20parties%20involved%20hold%20out%20the%20hope%20that%20their%20votes%20are%20transferable%20to%20their%20alliance%20partners.%20If%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%2C%20BSP%20and%20Congress%20put%20up%20one%20single%20candidate%20from%20the%20SP%2C%20the%20idea%20is%20that%20Congress%20and%20BSP%20voters%20from%20that%20constituency%20would%20also%20switch%20over%20to%20the%20SP.%20This%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20always%20the%20case.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%202019%2C%20the%20SP%20and%20BSP%20alliance%20appeared%20to%20have%20worked.%20The%20SP%20and%20BSP%20votes%20were%20transferable%20and%20the%20BJP%20lost%20some%20seats%20they%20had%20won%20in%202014.%20The%20same%20logic%20did%20not%20work%20in%20Karnataka%20in%202019%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20Secular%20(JDS)%20fought%20together.%20Here%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2026%20out%20of%20the%2028%20seats%2C%20a%20big%20improvement%20from%202014%2C%20when%20it%20won%2017.%20The%20success%20of%20pre-poll%20alliances%20relies%20on%20more%20than%20just%20arithmetic.%20Chemistry%20is%20a%20very%20important%20factor.%20While%20leaders%20may%20coordinate%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20is%20there%20a%20similar%20level%20of%20synergy%20there%20amongst%20cadres%20on%20the%20ground%3F%20If%20this%20chemistry%20is%20absent%2C%20the%20alliance%20is%20likely%20to%20fail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20fallout%20between%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%20is%20also%20an%20indication%20of%20fundamental%20contradictions.%20In%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20Trinamool%20and%20CPM%20are%20bitter%20political%20rivals.%20Would%20the%20three%20parties%20set%20aside%20their%20contradicting%20political%20interests%20and%20come%20up%20with%20a%20common%20seat%20sharing%20formula%3F%20Recent%20developments%20suggest%20that%20is%20clearly%20not%20the%20case.%20Though%20there%20was%20a%20fragile%20truce%20until%20now%2C%20the%20differences%20erupted%20when%20the%20question%20of%20seat%20sharing%20came%20up.%20A%20similar%20story%20plays%20out%20in%20Punjab.%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20political%20rivals%20in%20the%20state.%20More%20importantly%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20a%20very%20small%20electoral%20presence%20in%20Punjab.%20It%20made%20no%20sense%20to%20AAP%20to%20agree%20on%20a%20seat%20sharing%20formula%20in%20Punjab%2C%20a%20state%20where%20they%20are%20the%20primary%20political%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20these%20differing%20political%20interests%2C%20there%20are%20fundamental%20ideological%20differences%20too.%20The%20Ram%20Mandir%20inauguration%20exposed%20these%20ideological%20differences.%20The%20Trinamool%20and%20Left%20Parties%20have%20taken%20a%20clear-cut%20stance%20on%20the%20issue.%20Sitaram%20Yechury's%20visit%20to%20Lenin's%20statue%20firmly%20underscores%20the%20Left's%20commitment%20to%20politics%20devoid%20of%20any%20involvement%20with%20religious%20identities.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20not%20distanced%20herself%20from%20religion%20but%20highlighted%20the%20need%20to%20engage%20with%20all%20faiths%20equally.%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20AAP%20have%20indicated%20a%20move%20towards%20'soft'%20Hindutva%2C%20positioning%20the%20party%20as%20a%20right-of-centre%20alternative%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Following%20AAP's%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20alliance%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20proclaimed%20that%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20was%20a%20'matter%20of%20pride'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20elections%20now%20just%20a%20few%20months%20away%2C%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20coalition%20seems%20to%20be%20unravelling%20at%20the%20worst%20possible%20time.%20The%20friction%20should%20not%20come%20as%20a%20surprise.%20There%20are%20fundamental%20internal%20contradictions%20between%20various%20partners%2C%20which%20are%20blowing%20up%20during%20discussions%20on%20seat%20sharing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20coalition%20manages%20to%20navigate%20these%20challenges%20will%20be%20crucial.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20the%20India%20coalition%20has%20its%20work%20cut%20out.%20Following%20the%20December%20election%20results%20and%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20the%20momentum%20appears%20to%20be%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20author%20is%20an%20Assistant%20Professor%20in%20the%20School%20of%20Humanities%20and%20Social%20Sciences%2C%20GITAM%20Deemed%20to%20be%20University%2C%20Visakhapatnam.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706523900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ftg2n9v3g_india-alliance-mumbai-meeting-650_625x300_01_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fend-of-the-road-for-the-i-n-d-i-a-grouping-4953290%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20grouping%20has%20multiple%20ideological%20and%20political%20contradictions%2C%20which%20were%20bound%20to%20surface%20at%20some%20point.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fend-of-the-road-for-the-i-n-d-i-a-grouping-4953290%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fend-of-the-road-for-the-i-n-d-i-a-grouping-4953290%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fend-of-the-road-for-the-i-n-d-i-a-grouping-4953290%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Election%20Season%2C%20Who%20Gets%20to%20Take%20the%20Credit%20for%20Jobs%20and%20Reservation%20in%20Bihar%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F05184147%2FFxHyj_3aEAMGYQ6.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20taken%20away%20Nitish%20Kumar%20from%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20is%20for%20all%20to%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20election%20season%2C%20will%20the%20Nitish-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20government%20in%20Bihar%20be%20able%20to%20take%20away%20the%20credit%20for%20giving%20four%20lakh%20jobs%20and%20hiking%20the%20quota%20for%20the%20marginalised%20classes%20up%20to%2065%25%20from%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20its%20leader%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeteran%20socialist%20leader%20and%20RJD%20national%20vice-president%20Shivanand%20Tivary%20said%20it%20will%20be%20impossible%20for%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20the%20BJP%20to%20spin%20these%20as%20successes%20of%20just%20Nitish%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20caste-survey%2C%20the%20raising%20of%20reservation%20to%2065%25%20and%20giving%20jobs%20on%20a%20huge%20scale%20are%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20cause%20of%20social%20justice%20that%20is%20central%20to%20RJD%E2%80%99s%20politics.%20Nitish%20was%20compelled%20to%20do%20it%20by%20Tejashwi%2C%20who%20had%20promised%20the%20same%20in%20the%202020%20assembly%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tivary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejashwi%2C%20who%20has%20now%20lost%20his%20position%20as%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20had%20explicitly%20promised%20to%20give%2010%20lakh%20jobs%20in%20the%20event%20of%20coming%20to%20power%20in%202020%20assembly%20polls.%20His%20promise%20clicked.%20The%20RJD%20emerging%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20party%2C%20with%2079%20MLAs.%20Nitish%20whose%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20was%20reduced%20to%2045%20seats%20in%20those%20polls%20had%20purportedly%20wondered%20in%20close%20circles%20as%20to%20where%20Tejashwi%20thought%20he%20would%20get%20the%20money%20to%20deliver%20this%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20dumped%20the%20BJP%20and%20shifted%20to%20the%20RJD-Congress-Left%20alliance%20on%20August%209%2C%202022.%20In%20his%20Independence%20Day%20address%20on%20August%2015%2C%202022%2C%20Nitish%20announced%20that%20he%20would%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20implement%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20promise.%20By%20then%20Tejashwi%20had%20become%20his%20deputy%20and%20was%20present%20at%20the%20event.%20The%20chief%20minister%20promised%20%3Cem%3Emore%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ethan%3C%2Fem%3E%2010%20lakh%20jobs.%20He%20distributed%202.20%20lakh%20appointment%20letters%20to%20teachers%20in%20an%20unparalleled%20spectacle%20at%20Patna%E2%80%99s%20Gandhi%20Maidan%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20education%20department%20which%20was%20understood%20to%20be%20under%20the%20RJD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flight%20of%20Nitish%20to%20the%20BJP%20on%20Sunday%2C%20January%2028%2C%20was%20preceded%20by%20an%20advertisement%20war%20on%20the%20credit%20for%20development%20in%20Bihar.%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20image%20had%20notably%20been%20missing%20on%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20advertisements%2C%20which%20had%20carried%20the%20picture%20of%20the%20CM%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20irked%20RJD%20cadres%20who%20displayed%20pictures%20of%20Tejashwi%20with%20a%20list%20of%20his%20achievements%20at%20the%20RJD%20headquarters%20in%20retaliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fayaram-gayaram-politics-of-nitish-at-play-poised-to-rejoin-nda%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fayaram-gayaram-politics-of-nitish-at-play-poised-to-rejoin-nda%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3EAyaram%20Gayaram%20Politics%20of%20Nitish%20at%20Play%2C%20Poised%20to%20Rejoin%20NDA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20BJP-JD(U)%E2%80%99s%20strategists%20were%20at%20work%20to%20take%20%E2%80%93%20along%20with%20Nitish%20%E2%80%93%20the%20credit%20for%20giving%20jobs%20became%20evident%20when%20the%20CM%20in%20his%20first%20statement%20after%20switching%20sides%20to%20the%20BJP%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20working%20hard%20for%20Bihar%20and%20they%20%5Bwithout%20naming%20RJD%5D%20were%20interested%20in%20taking%20credit%20alone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Tejashwi%20said%20that%20the%20CM%20had%20a%20problem%20with%20RJD%20getting%20the%20credit%20for%20its%20achievements.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20the%20largest%20component%20of%20the%20grand%20alliance%20government.%20We%20had%20education%2C%20health%2C%20tourism%2C%20sports%20and%20other%20key%20departments%20in%20our%20quota.%20The%20RJD%20ministers%20worked%20hard%20to%20fulfil%20our%20promises%20to%20the%20people.%20How%20could%20we%20be%20denied%20the%20credit%20for%20our%20work%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESocial%20justice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20the%20BJP%20claims%2C%20it%20is%20a%20fact%20that%20the%20Hindutva%20party%20was%20feeling%20hugely%20insecure%20in%20Bihar%20with%20Nitish%20Kumar%20on%20the%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20side.%20Bihar%20under%20the%20alliance%20had%20produced%20what%20looked%20like%20a%20potent%20counter-narrative%20with%20the%20centrality%20of%20social%20justice%20in%20its%20operations.%20It%20appeared%20to%20make%20good%20on%20the%20promise%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3Ejiski%20jitni%20bhagidari%2C%20uski%20utni%20hissedari%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20proportionate%20representation%20to%20the%20marginalised%20classes%20in%20governance%20apparatus.%20Issues%20of%20disparity%2C%20deprivation%2C%20livelihood%2C%20health%20and%20sustenance%20concerning%20the%20common%20people%20took%20prominence%20against%20Hindutva%20politics%20which%20aggressively%20pursued%20religious%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECreating%20buzz%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Hindu%20deity%20Ram%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20confident%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20juggernaut%20would%20sail%20through%20smoothly%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%20But%20that%20it%20might%20be%20stuck%20in%20Bihar%20%E2%80%93%20where%20with%20Nitish%20BJP%20had%20bagged%2039%20seats%20out%20of%2040%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20was%20not%20lost%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20core%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cinsecurity%E2%80%9D%20was%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20RJD%E2%80%99s%20proven%20track%20record%20as%20a%20champion%20of%20social%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20novelty%20of%20Tejashwi%20was%20he%20had%20added%20economic%20justice%20%E2%80%93%20emphasising%20on%20jobs%2C%20sports%2C%20tourism%2C%20IT%20and%20investment%20%E2%80%93%20to%20expanding%20on%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20battle%20for%20social%20justice%20and%20attracting%20youths%20to%20his%20party.%20Much%20ahead%20of%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20the%20alliance%2C%20the%20RJD%20under%20the%20stewardship%20of%20Tejashwi%20was%20demanding%20caste%20surveys%2C%20raising%20the%20quota%20for%20the%20backward%20classes%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20while%20at%20once%20launching%20a%20frontal%20attack%20on%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20issues%20of%20radical%20Hindutva%2C%20the%20subverting%20constitution%2C%20subjugating%20democratic%20institutions%20and%20misusing%20investigating%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwith-job-mahakumbha-nitish-kumar-foregrounds-importance-of-promises-kept%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwith-job-mahakumbha-nitish-kumar-foregrounds-importance-of-promises-kept%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3EWith%20Job%20%E2%80%98Mahakumbha%E2%80%99%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Foregrounds%20Importance%20of%20Promises%20Kept%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOstensibly%2C%20Nitish%20carrying%20the%20socialist%20legacy%20was%20favourable%20to%20the%20social%20justice%20plank.%20But%20he%20was%20able%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20caste%20survey%2C%20raise%20the%20reservation%20limit%20up%20to%2065%25%20and%20give%20employment%20on%20a%20huge%20scale%20to%20the%20youths%20only%20after%20he%20joined%20the%20alliance.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20Caste%20Census%20at%20the%20national%20level%20became%20the%20basis%20for%20the%20JDU-RJD%20alliance%20with%20Nitish%20and%20Tejashwi%20forwarding%20this%20demand%20to%20the%20Union%20government.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20government%20opposed%20the%20caste%20survey%20in%20Bihar%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20subsequently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20and%20reservation%20limit%20raise%20provided%20the%20first%20potent%20template%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20to%20counter%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20drive.%20In%20fact%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20despite%20the%20veiled%20objections%20from%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20old%20guards%2C%20adopted%20the%20Bihar%20%E2%80%98model%E2%80%99%20and%20promised%20the%20Caste%20Census%20in%20his%20campaigns%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20these%20three%20states%20in%20the%20recent%20assembly%20polls%20and%20tried%20to%20create%20the%20perception%20that%20Hindutva%20politics%20had%20defeated%20%E2%80%9Ccaste%20politics%E2%80%9D.%20But%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20the%20Congress%20upped%20or%20retained%20its%20vote-percentage%20as%20it%20lost%20marginally%20in%20terms%20of%20votes%2C%20if%20not%20in%20terms%20of%20seats%2C%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBharat%20Ratna%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20putting%20up%20a%20brave%20face%2C%20the%20Hindutva%20party%20was%2C%20apparently%2C%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20fear%20about%20the%20social%20justice%20plank%2C%20at%20least%2C%20in%20Bihar%20which%20had%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20holding%20on%20to%20his%20strength%20with%20the%20backward%20classes%20and%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalu%20had%20decisively%20defeated%20the%20BJP%20in%20all%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20assembly%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20%E2%80%93%20from%201991%20to%202004%20when%20the%20Hindutva%20party%20under%20L.K%20Advani%20and%20A.B%20Vajpayee%20had%20made%20reasonable%20inroads%20in%20other%20states%20of%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%2C%20including%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20And%20despite%20his%20party%20losing%20power%20to%20Nitish%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%202005%2C%20Lalu%E2%80%99s%20RJD%20stayed%20strong%20with%20its%20support%20of%20the%20backward%20classes%20including%20the%20Yadavs%20who%20are%20the%20single%20largest%20backward%20caste%20and%20the%20minorities%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20symbolic%20as%20well%20as%20substantive%20reasons%20to%20fear%20the%20prospect%20of%20Lalu%20united%20with%20Nitish.%20Even%20if%20Nitish%20was%20reduced%20to%2015%25%20vote-share%20in%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20his%20presence%20in%20the%20alliance%20could%20have%20been%20the%20%E2%80%9Cplus%E2%80%9D%20factor%20to%20the%20alliance%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20calculating%20all%20these%20factors%20that%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20conferred%20upon%20Karpoori%20Thakur%20%E2%80%93%20the%20father%20of%20the%20social%20justice%20movement%20%E2%80%93%20posthumously%2C%20a%20day%20after%20Narendra%20Modi%20consecrated%20the%20Ram%20temple%20at%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Nitish%20had%20thanked%20the%20PM