%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20made%20the%20remark%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Assam's%20Dhubri%20when%20he%20was%20targeting%20Mr%20Sarma%20over%20corruption.%20Alleging%20that%20the%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20the%20country's%20most%20corrupt%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20has%20a%20cut%20in%20every%20business%2C%20including%20coal%20and%20tea%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20wake%20up%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20put%20coal%20on%20the%20stove%20to%20prepare%20tea%2C%20the%20profit%20from%20coal%20goes%20to%20your%20Chief%20Minister.%20The%20tea%20which%20you%20drink%2C%20its%20plantations%20and%20gardens%20belong%20to%20your%20chief%20minister.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20state%20Congress%20is%20yet%20to%20respond%20to%20Mr%20Adhikary's%20derogatory%20remark%2C%20apparently%20because%20they%20are%20busy%20with%20the%20yatra%2C%20its%20INDIA%20ally%20Trinamool%20has%20used%20the%20opportunity%20to%20target%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%2C%20particularly%2C%20the%20Congress's%20state%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20a%20video%20clip%20of%20Mr%20Adhikari's%20remark%2C%20Trinamool%20leader%20and%20spokesperson%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20language%20is%20the%20traitor%20using%20to%20target%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20Such%20uncouth%20behaviour%20in%20politics%20must%20stop.%20How%20low%20will%20state%20Congress%20leaders%20acting%20as%20BJP's%20pimps%20stoop%3F%20Will%20you%20take%20this%20lying%20down%3F%20Suvendu's%20politics%20has%20no%20shame%20now.%20I%20protest%20this%20sick%20language.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Btraitor%26quot%3B%20reference%20is%20Trinamool's%20signature%20barb%20at%20Mr%20Adhikari%2C%20once%20a%20trusted%20lieutenant%20of%20party%20supremo%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20who%20then%20switched%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20became%20an%20arch-rival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20leader's%20remark%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20tug-of-war%20between%20his%20party%20and%20the%20Congress%20over%20seat-sharing%20in%20INDIA%20alliance.%20Virtually%20pulling%20the%20plug%20on%20an%20alliance%20in%20Bengal%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20last%20week%20said%20her%20party%20will%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20alone%20and%20any%20decision%20on%20an%20alliance%20will%20be%20taken%20after%20the%20election.%20The%20Congress%20has%20since%20been%20in%20damage%20control%20mode%20and%20has%20said%20INDIA%20bloc%20cannot%20be%20imagined%20without%20Ms%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20leadership%20has%20repeatedly%20blamed%20the%20local%20Congress%20unit%2C%20helmed%20by%20the%20party's%20Lok%20Sabha%20leader%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20for%20the%20impasse%20over%20seat-sharing.%20The%20party%20has%2C%20in%20the%20past%2C%20also%20accused%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20of%20being%20a%20%26quot%3BBJP%20agent%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chowdhury%20has%20been%20fiercely%20critical%20of%20Ms%20Banerjee%2C%20calling%20her%20an%20%26quot%3Bopportunist%26quot%3B%20and%20rejecting%20the%20Trinamool's%20offer%20of%20two%20seats%20as%20part%20of%20the%20seat-sharing%20arrangement.%20The%20Trinamool%20maintains%20that%20it%20has%20been%20quite%20generous%20in%20its%20offer%20and%20criticised%20the%20Congress%20for%20the%20delay%20in%20reaching%20an%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706521140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-05%2F7m97k4e8_suvendu-adhikari-facebook_625x300_20_May_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsuvendu-adhikari-rahul-gandhi-bengal-bjp-leader-uses-slang-for-rahul-gandhi-trinamool-slips-in-a-swipe-4953178%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengal%20BJP%20leader%20Suvendu%20Adhikari's%20derogatory%20remark%20on%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20provided%20an%20opportunity%20to%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20to%20take%20a%20swipe%20at%20state%20Congress%20leaders%20amid%20a%20tussle%20over%20seat-sharing%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll