arks%20the%20second%20suicide%20in%20January%2C%20underscores%20the%20escalating%20issue%20of%20exam%20stress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-am-loser-another-student-dies-by-suicide-in-rajasthans-kota-4952956%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-am-loser-another-student-dies-by-suicide-in-rajasthans-kota-4952956%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-am-loser-another-student-dies-by-suicide-in-rajasthans-kota-4952956%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Charting%20The%20Course%20Of%20Infrastructure%20Transformation%20In%20The%20Modi%20Era%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInfrastructure%20development%20plays%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20driving%20long-term%20economic%20growth%20by%20enhancing%20productivity%2C%20improving%20living%20standards%2C%20and%20fostering%20sustainable%20expansion.%20Classical%20and%20neoclassical%20theories%20highlight%20the%20importance%20of%20infrastructure%20in%20increasing%20the%20productive%20capacity%20of%20an%20economy%2C%20as%20efficient%20transportation%2C%20communication%20networks%2C%20and%20energy%20distribution%20systems%20reduce%20operational%20costs%20and%20enhance%20competitiveness.%20Meanwhile%2C%20endogenous%20growth%20theory%20emphasizes%20the%20role%20of%20infrastructure%20investments%20in%20promoting%20technological%20innovation%20and%20human%20capital%20development%2C%20with%20education%20and%20research%20facilities%20sparking%20innovations%20that%20propel%20growth.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20new%20economic%20geography%20underscores%20infrastructure's%20significance%20in%20connecting%20remote%20areas%20with%20economic%20hubs%2C%20facilitating%20regional%20development%2C%20and%20ensuring%20more%20balanced%20economic%20growth%20across%20different%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20sustainable%20economic%20advancement%2C%20the%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20infrastructure%20projects%20with%20high%20multiplier%20effects%2C%20such%20as%20transportation%20networks%2C%20renewable%20energy%20sources%2C%20water%20and%20sanitation%20systems%2C%20digital%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20educational%20and%20health%20facilities.%20These%20investments%20not%20only%20provide%20immediate%20employment%20opportunities%20and%20stimulate%20economic%20demand%20but%20also%20lay%20the%20groundwork%20for%20future%20prosperity%20by%20boosting%20efficiency%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20human%20capital.%20Such%20strategic%20infrastructure%20development%20is%20essential%20for%20achieving%20long-term%20economic%20objectives%2C%20as%20it%20not%20only%20meets%20immediate%20needs%20but%20also%20addresses%20future%20challenges%20and%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20critique%20of%20short-term%2C%20inefficient%20investments%2C%20illustrated%20by%20Keynes'%20metaphor%20of%20%26quot%3Bdigging%20holes%20and%20filling%20them%20up%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20underscores%20the%20necessity%20of%20prioritizing%20projects%20that%20yield%20substantial%20and%20enduring%20economic%20benefits.%20While%20Keynes%20advocated%20for%20government%20spending%20to%20stimulate%20demand%20during%20downturns%2C%20he%20cautioned%20against%20wasteful%20expenditures.%20Instead%2C%20the%20emphasis%20should%20be%20on%20sustainable%20infrastructure%20projects%20that%20not%20only%20provide%20a%20short-term%20economic%20boost%20but%20also%20contribute%20to%20long-term%20growth%20by%20enhancing%20the%20overall%20productivity%20and%20competitiveness%20of%20the%20economy.%20This%20approach%20aligns%20with%20broader%20economic%20theories%20that%20stress%20the%20critical%20role%20of%20strategic%20infrastructure%20investment%20in%20supporting%20long-term%20development%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20equitable%20regional%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20precisely%20what%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20done.%20Since%20Narendra%20Modi%20took%20office%20in%202014%2C%20infrastructure%20development%20has%20been%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20his%20government's%20economic%20strategy%2C%20significantly%20impacting%20India's%20growth%20trajectory.%20The%20Modi%20administration%20has%20prioritized%20large-scale%20infrastructure%20projects%2C%20including%20the%20development%20of%20highways%2C%20railways%2C%20airports%2C%20smart%20cities%2C%20and%20digital%20infrastructure%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20enhancing%20connectivity%2C%20improving%20efficiency%2C%20and%20attracting%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202023%2C%20the%20national%20highway%20network%20had%20increased%20by%2060%25%20from%20its%20extent%20in%202014%2C%20showcasing%20the%20government's%20commitment%20to%20infrastructure%20development.%20Specifically%2C%20the%20length%20of%20national%20highways%20increased%20from%2091%2C287%20km%20in%202014%20to%20146%2C145%20km%20by%202023.%20The%20pace%20of%20construction%20has%20been%20noteworthy%2C%20with%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20maintaining%20a%20construction%20pace%20of%2020.78%20km%20per%20day%20during%20the%20first%20seven%20months%20of%20the%20financial%20year%202023-24.%20This%20is%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20initiative%20to%20construct%2012%2C500%20km%20of%20highways%20within%20the%20year.%20For%20context%2C%20the%20annual%20highway%20construction%20achievements%20in%20the%20years%20leading%20up%20to%202023%20included%2010%2C237%20km%20in%202019-20%2C%2013%2C327%20km%20in%202020-21%2C%20and%2010%2C457%20km%20in%202021-22.%20This%20marked%20increase%20in%20highway%20construction%20under%20the%20Modi%20government%20contrasts%20with%20the%20pace%20before%202014%2C%20indicating%20a%20robust%20focus%20on%20building%20infrastructure%20as%20a%20means%20to%20bolster%20economic%20growth%20and%20connectivity%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20efforts%20are%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20Bharatmala%20Pariyojana%2C%20an%20ambitious%20program%20aimed%20at%20developing%20about%2034%2C800%20km%20of%20highways%20across%20India.%20The%20initiative%20reflects%20the%20government's%20strategy%20to%20improve%20transportation%2C%20facilitate%20trade%2C%20and%20enhance%20accessibility%2C%20thereby%20contributing%20to%20the%20nation's%20socio-economic%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20since%202014%2C%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20has%20embarked%20on%20a%20transformative%20journey%2C%20marked%20by%20significant%20increases%20in%20capital%20expenditure%20and%20ambitious%20modernization%20efforts.%20The%20period%20has%20seen%20record%20investments%20in%20railway%20infrastructure%2C%20including%20the%20rollout%20of%20modern%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%20trains%2C%20accelerated%20station%20redevelopment%20under%20the%20Amrit%20Bharat%20scheme%2C%20and%20a%20notable%20push%20towards%20electrification%20and%20track%20laying.%20The%20Gross%20Budgetary%20Support%20(GBS)%20for%20the%20railways%20saw%20a%20quantum%20leap%20in%202023-24%2C%20reaching%20Rs%202.4%20lakh%20crore%2C%20highlighting%20the%20government's%20commitment%20to%20enhancing%20the%20rail%20network's%20capacity%20and%20efficiency.%20This%20investment%20is%20a%20substantial%20increase%20from%20previous%20years%2C%20demonstrating%20a%20strategic%20focus%20on%20leveraging%20the%20railways%20to%20drive%20economic%20growth%20and%20improve%20connectivity%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20period%20before%202014%2C%20under%20the%20UPA%20government%2C%20saw%20more%20modest%20investments%20in%20railway%20infrastructure.%20The%20GBS%20in%20the%20railway%20budget%20for%202004-05%20was%20Rs%208%2C000%20crore%2C%20and%20for%202013-14%20it%20was%20Rs%2029%2C055%20crore%2C%20indicating%20a%20more%20conservative%20approach%20to%20railway%20development.%20The%20Modi%20government's%20approach%20marks%20a%20significant%20departure%20from%20the%20past%2C%20focusing%20not%20just%20on%20expanding%20the%20rail%20network%20but%20also%20on%20modernizing%20it%20with%20advanced%20technology%20and%20services.%20This%20includes%20the%20extensive%20rollout%20of%20Vande%20Bharat%20trains%2C%20which%20are%20indigenously%20designed%20semi-high%20speed%20trains%2C%20and%20the%20fast-tracking%20of%20major%20infrastructure%20projects%20like%20the%20redevelopment%20of%20stations%20and%20the%20laying%20of%20new%20tracks.%20The%20emphasis%20on%20modernization%20and%20high-capacity%20infrastructure%20reflects%20a%20strategic%20shift%20towards%20making%20Indian%20Railways%20a%20world-class%20transporter%2C%20ready%20to%20meet%20the%20future%20demands%20of%20a%20rapidly%20growing%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20union%20government%20is%20also%20addressing%20the%20regional%20infrastructure%20development%20disparity.%20Since%202014%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20significantly%20increased%20infrastructure%20development%20in%20the%20North%20Eastern%20Region%20(NER)%2C%20marking%20a%20substantial%20shift%20from%20the%20initiatives%20undertaken%20prior%20to%202014%20under%20the%20UPA%20government.%20An%20impressive%20sum%20of%20Rs.%203.84%20lakh%20crore%20has%20been%20allocated%20by%2055%20non-exempted%20Central%20Ministries%2FDepartments%20for%20infrastructure%20projects%20in%20the%20NER%2C%20including%20Assam%2C%20leveraging%20at%20least%2010%25%20of%20their%20Gross%20Budgetary%20Support%20(GBS)%20for%20this%20purpose.%20This%20expenditure%20has%20facilitated%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20projects%2C%20from%20road%20construction%2C%20where%204%2C121%20km%20of%20road%20projects%20have%20been%20completed%2C%20to%20the%20sanctioning%20of%20Rs.%2019%2C855%20crore%20for%20new%20rail%20projects%2C%20enhancing%20both%20road%20and%20rail%20connectivity%20in%20the%20region.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20telecommunications%20infrastructure%20has%20been%20bolstered%20with%20the%20installation%20of%201%2C358%20towers%20covering%201%2C246%20villages%2C%20and%201%2C195%20projects%20worth%20Rs.%2015%2C375%20crore%20have%20been%20sanctioned%20under%20the%20schemes%20of%20MDoNER%20and%20NEC%20in%20the%20NER%20States%2C%20including%20Assam%2C%20from%202014-2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20approach%20contrasts%20starkly%20with%20the%20period%20before%202014%2C%20where%20infrastructure%20development%20in%20the%20NER%20was%20less%20pronounced%20and%20less%20integrated.%20The%20comprehensive%20and%20multi-modal%20nature%20of%20the%20projects%20initiated%20since%202014-encompassing%20road%2C%20rail%2C%20air%2C%20waterway%2C%20telecom%2C%20and%20power%20connectivity-reflects%20a%20more%20holistic%20and%20concerted%20effort%20to%20bring%20the%20NER%20into%20the%20mainstream%20of%20national%20development.%20The%20focus%20has%20not%20only%20been%20on%20enhancing%20connectivity%20but%20also%20on%20ensuring%20that%20these%20infrastructure%20developments%20are%20sustainable%20and%20cater%20to%20the%20long-term%20needs%20of%20the%20region%2C%20thus%20setting%20a%20new%20precedent%20for%20focused%20regional%20development%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20power%20sector%2C%20India%20has%20made%20remarkable%20strides%2C%20transitioning%20from%20a%20power%20deficit%20to%20a%20power%20surplus%20nation.%20The%20average%20availability%20of%20power%20has%20significantly%20improved%2C%20reaching%2020.5%20hours%20in%20rural%20areas%20and%2023.5%20hours%20in%20urban%20areas.%20This%20achievement%20is%20poised%20to%20make%20generating%20sets%20and%20stabilizers%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%20Additionally%2C%20India%20has%20become%20a%20global%20leader%20in%20the%20cost-effective%20production%20of%20renewable%20energy%2C%20boasting%20the%20cheapest%20renewable%20energy%20production%20costs%20worldwide.%20This%20focus%20on%20renewable%20energy%20is%20part%20of%20India's%20broader%20commitment%20to%20sustainable%20development%20and%20energy%20security.%20The%20nation%20has%20achieved%20its%20NDC%20target%20of%20having%2040%25%20of%20its%20installed%20electricity%20capacity%20from%20non-fossil%20fuel%20sources%20nine%20years%20ahead%20of%20schedule%2C%20in%202021.%20This%20achievement%20underscores%20India's%20commitment%20to%20combating%20climate%20change%20and%20transitioning%20towards%20a%20green%20economy.%20The%20rapid%20expansion%20in%20solar%20capacity%2C%20which%20has%20increased%2023-fold%20since%202014%2C%20along%20with%20the%20distribution%20of%20nearly%2090%20lakh%20solar%20lighting%20systems%2C%20reflects%20the%20government's%20focus%20on%20harnessing%20solar%20energy%20to%20meet%20its%20power%20needs.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20deployment%20of%20over%205.3%20lakh%20solar%20pumps%20to%20farmers%20signifies%20a%20push%20towards%20sustainable%20agricultural%20practices.%20The%20reduction%20in%20solar%20tariffs%20to%20below%20Rs.%202%20per%20unit%20highlights%20the%20economic%20viability%20of%20renewable%20energy%2C%20making%20it%20an%20attractive%20investment%20and%20further%20driving%20India's%20renewable%20energy%20sector%20forward.%20This%20concerted%20push%20towards%20renewable%20energy%20is%20a%20key%20component%20of%20India's%20infrastructure%20development%2C%20aligning%20with%20global%20sustainability%20goals%20and%20ensuring%20energy%20security%20for%20future%20generations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlongside%20the%20notable%20advancements%20in%20power%20and%20transportation%20infrastructure%2C%20India's%20focus%20on%20telecommunications%20and%20digital%20infrastructure%20has%20been%20transformative.%20The%20government's%20efforts%20have%20led%20to%20a%20drastic%20reduction%20in%20mobile%20data%20tariffs%2C%20from%20Rs%20269%20per%20GB%20in%202014%20to%20Rs%2010.1%20per%20GB%2C%20making%20digital%20connectivity%20more%20accessible%20to%20a%20broader%20segment%20of%20the%20population.%20This%20reduction%20in%20costs%20has%20spurred%20a%20remarkable%20increase%20in%20data%20consumption%2C%20which%20has%20grown%2063%20times%2C%20and%20the%20number%20of%20mobile%20broadband%20subscribers%20has%20expanded%20more%20than%2017%20times.%20Such%20developments%20are%20pivotal%20in%20driving%20India's%20digital%20revolution%2C%20making%20information%20and%20digital%20services%20more%20accessible%20and%20fostering%20inclusive%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comprehensive%20approach%20to%20infrastructure%20development%20under%20PM%20Modi's%20leadership%20reflects%20a%20strategic%20vision%20to%20transform%20India%20into%20a%20developed%20nation%20with%20future-ready%20infrastructure.%20This%20vision%20encompasses%20not%20just%20the%20physical%20infrastructure%20but%20also%20the%20digital%20and%20energy%20landscapes%2C%20ensuring%20that%20India's%20growth%20is%20sustainable%2C%20inclusive%2C%20and%20resilient.%20The%20government's%20concerted%20efforts%20in%20these%20areas%20are%20setting%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20new%20era%20of%20prosperity%20and%20global%20competitiveness%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBibek%20Debroy%20is%20the%20Chairman%2C%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20(EAC-PM)%20%26amp%3B%20Aditya%20Sinha%20is%20Additional%20Private%20Secretary%20(Policy%20%26amp%3B%20Research)%2C%20EAC-PM.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706520600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F4l4i1e1g_narendra-modi-ani_625x300_03_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcharting-the-course-of-infrastructure-transformation-in-the-modi-era-4671928%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Infrastructure%20development%20plays%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20driving%20long-term%20economic%20growth%20by%20enhancing%20productivity%2C%20improving%20living%20standards%2C%20and%20fostering%20sustainable%20expansion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcharting-the-course-of-infrastructure-transformation-in-the-modi-era-4671928%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcharting-the-course-of-infrastructure-transformation-in-the-modi-era-4671928%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcharting-the-course-of-infrastructure-transformation-in-the-modi-era-4671928%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20The%20Strong%20Political%20Message%20Behind%20Macron's%20India%20Visit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPresident%20Emmanuel%20Macron's%20visit%20to%20India%20as%20chief%20guest%20at%20our%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations%20had%20a%20ceremonial%20aspect%2C%20no%20doubt%2C%20but%20in%20relations%20between%20states%20ceremonial%20gestures%20convey%20a%20message%20at%20many%20levels%20-%20of%20an%20honour%20deserved%2C%20importance%20of%20the%20relationship%2C%20an%20investment%20into%20the%20future%2C%20expected%20benefits%2C%20a%20signal%20to%20others%2C%20and%20the%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20was%20f%C3%AAted%20by%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20in%20June%202023%2C%20it%20conveyed%20a%20strong%20political%20message%20at%20the%20bilateral%20and%20international%20levels%2C%20of%20the%20US%20wooing%20India%20for%20larger%20strategic%20goals.%20Ceremony%20is%20part%20of%20diplomacy%20and%20is%20not%20without%20substance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20himself%20was%20Guest%20of%20Honour%20on%20Bastille%20Day%20(July%2014)%20in%20Paris%20in%202023.%20That%20honour%20was%20to%20convey%20France's%20desire%20to%20build%20stronger%20all-round%20ties%20with%20India.%20It%20was%20an%20investment%20in%20the%20future%20in%20view%20of%20India's%20growing%20economy%2C%20its%20diplomatic%20prowess%2C%20and%20shared%20strategic%20interests%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20in%20particular.%20Building%20more%20common%20ground%20with%20India%20on%20climate%20change%20issues%2C%20which%20is%20a%20prime%20area%20of%20debate%20and%20concern%20in%20French%20society%20(Modi%20and%20Macron%20reaffirmed%20in%20the%20joint%20statement%20their%20commitment%20to%20come%20forward%20in%20their%20next%20nationally%20determined%20contributions%20with%20ambitious%20targets%2C%20with%20France%20commending%20India's%20offer%20to%20host%20COP%2033%20in%202028)%20is%20an%20important%20French%20objective.%20So%20is%20leveraging%20French%20capabilities%20to%20foster%20links%20with%20increasing%20Indian%20capabilities%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20defence%2C%20advanced%20technologies%20and%20the%20digital%20domain%2C%20using%20India%20as%20a%20springboard%20for%20reaching%20out%20more%20to%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20which%20is%20becoming%20more%20vocal%20and%20demanding%20with%20regard%20to%20its%20interests%20in%20the%20hitherto%20west-dominated%20global%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20India%20drawing%20closer%20to%20the%20US%20and%20its%20Quad%20membership%2C%20France%2C%20which%20has%20major%20interests%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20seeks%20to%20carve%20out%20an%20independent%20role%20for%20itself%20and%20not%20let%20itself%20be%20subsumed%20under%20US-led%20structures.%20This%2C%20to%20mark%20its%20attachment%20to%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20autonomy%26quot%3B.%20In%20pursuing%20this%2C%20India%20is%20an%20obvious%20partner.%20For%20India%20too%2C%20a%20closer%20strategic%20partnership%20with%20France%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20is%20diplomatically%20important%20as%20it%20conveys%20the%20message%20that%20security%20concerns%20in%20this%20region%20are%20also%20shared%20by%20a%20major%20European%20power%2C%20and%20not%20US%2C%20Australia%20and%20Japan%20alone.%20In%20the%20joint%20statement%2C%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region's%20significance%20for%20the%20respective%20sovereign%20and%20strategic%20interests%20of%20France%20and%20India%20has%20been%20emphasised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20statement%20says%20explicitly%2C%20%26quot%3BDefense%20and%20security%20partnership%20has%20been%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20the%20India-France%20partnership%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%26quot%3B.%20This%20is%20meaningful%2C%20as%20the%20security%20threat%20in%20this%20region%20emanates%20from%20China.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20his%20banquet%20speech%2C%20Macron%20referred%20to%20the%20activities%20of%20%26quot%3Bsome%20hegemonic%20powers%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%20The%20two%20sides%20have%20also%20agreed%20to%20intensify%20their%20cooperation%20in%20the%20Southwest%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20building%20on%20the%20joint%20surveillance%20missions%20carried%20out%20from%20La%20Reunion%20in%202020%20and%202022.%20Significantly%2C%20they%20plan%20to%20extend%20those%20interactions%20in%20India's%20maritime%20neighbourhood%20to%20contribute%20positively%20to%20the%20securitisation%20of%20strategic%20sea%20lanes%20of%20communication.%20The%20two%20sides%20have%20also%20committed%20to%20revitalizing%20the%20trilateral%20cooperation%20with%20Australia%2C%20deepen%20the%20one%20with%20UAE%2C%20and%20explore%20new%20ones%20in%20the%20region.%20They%20have%20agreed%20to%20explore%20opportunities%20for%20coordinating%20economic%20projects%20and%20programmes%20in%20the%20Pacific%2C%20which%20marks%20an%20extension%20of%20India's%20role%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20statement%20notes%20that%20%26quot%3Bsince%20the%20declaration%20of%20the%20Strategic%20Partnership%20in%201998%2C%20India%20and%20France%20have%20developed%20a%20partnership%20of%20exceptional%20trust%20and%20confidence%2C%20consistency%20and%20strength%26quot%3B.%20The%20word%20%26quot%3Bexceptional%26quot%3B%20is%20noteworthy.%20The%20references%20to%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20autonomy%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Ba%20shared%20commitment%20to%20a%20multipolar%20world%26quot%3B%20may%20seem%20predictable%20phrases%2C%20but%20they%20do%20convey%20the%20desire%20of%20both%20sides%20to%20exercise%20some%20independence%20at%20the%20strategic%20level%2C%20consonant%20with%20their%20national%20interests.%20Macron%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20is%20of%20the%20view%20that%20US%20policy%20on%20Taiwan%20is%20needlessly%20provocative%20and%20that%20France%20does%20not%20want%20to%20be%20a%20camp%20follower%20of%20the%20US%20in%20such%20questionable%20policies.%20This%20implies%20that%20France%20understands%20India's%20decision%20to%20protect%20its%20strategic%20ties%20with%20Russia%20even%20though%20France%20itself%20is%20increasingly%20at%20loggerheads%20with%20Moscow%20over%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict.%20The%20wording%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%20in%20the%20joint%20statement%20is%20careful%20and%20does%20not%20depart%20from%20the%20established%20Indian%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commitment%20to%20a%20multipolar%20world%20has%20been%20expressed%20by%20India%20and%20France%20over%20the%20years.%20For%20France%20it%20means%20a%20world%20that%20is%20not%20dominated%20entirely%20by%20the%20US%20and%20one%20in%20which%20Europe%20plays%20a%20strategic%20role%2C%20separate%20from%20the%20US%20based%20on%20its%20own%20priorities%20and%20interests%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20US%20when%20required.%20For%20India%2C%20multipolarity%20is%20essential%20for%20global%20rebalancing%2C%20to%20achieve%20UN%2C%20IMF%20and%20World%20Bank%20reforms%2C%20and%20for%20giving%20more%20weight%20to%20developing%20countries%20in%20international%20governance.%20India%20joins%20the%20BRICS%20and%20the%20SCO%20is%20support%20of%20multipolarity%20with%20this%20objective.%20India%2C%20of%20course%2C%20emphasises%20multipolarity%20in%20Asia%20as%20an%20essential%20step%20towards%20a%20multipolar%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20statement%20affirms%20France's%20support%20for%20India's%20candidacy%20to%20the%20International%20Energy%20Agency.%20The%20two%20countries%20have%20agreed%20to%20institute%20a%20Comprehensive%20Dialogue%20on%20Global%20Issues.%20The%20urgent%20need%20for%20the%20reform%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20and%20the%20early%20commencement%20of%20text-based%20negotiations%20at%20the%20Intergovernmental%20Negotiations%20(IGN)%20in%20the%20UN%20figures%20in%20joint%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron%20has%20congratulated%20Modi%20for%20his%20leadership%20in%20launching%20the%20historic%20initiative%20of%20the%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20Corridor%20(IMEC)%20on%20the%20margins%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20Delhi%20in%20September%202023.%20Modi%20has%20welcomed%20the%20appointment%20of%20President%20Macron's%20Special%20Envoy%20for%20the%20project%2C%20though%20this%20project%20will%20have%20to%20be%20shelved%20for%20the%20time%20being%20in%20view%20of%20the%20conflict%20in%20Gaza.%20While%20expressing%20solidarity%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%2C%20the%20two%20have%20condemned%20the%20huge%20loss%20of%20civilian%20lives%20in%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%2C%20and%20emphasised%20the%20need%20to%20respect%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20and%20to%20create%20conditions%2C%20including%20through%20a%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%2C%20for%20aid%20to%20flow%20to%20the%20affected%20population%20in%20the%20Gaza%20region.%20Both%20leaders%20have%20reaffirmed%20that%20a%20political%20process%20leading%20to%20a%20two-state%20solution%20for%20the%20Israeli%20and%20Palestinian%20people%20is%20required%20for%20lasting%20peace%20and%20stability%20in%20the%20region%2C%20besides%20expressing%20grave%20concern%20at%20the%20possibility%20of%20further%20expansion%20of%20the%20conflict%20in%20the%20region%2C%20including%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefence%20has%20always%20been%20a%20vital%20part%20of%20India-France%20ties%2C%20going%20back%20to%20the%201950s.%20Cynics%20have%20a%20tendency%20to%20say%20that%20France%20dresses%20up%20its%20ties%20with%20India%20with%20the%20sole%20purpose%20of%20selling%20more%20arms.%20This%20supposes%20that%20India%20has%20little%20agency%20in%20the%20matter%20and%20is%20manipulated%20into%20buying%20French%20defence%20equipment.%20The%20reality%20is%20that%20India%20sees%20France%20as%20a%20valuable%20defence%20partner%2C%20increasingly%20willing%20to%20transfer%20technology%2C%20one%20that%20has%20never%20applied%20sanctions%20on%20India%20or%20attached%20conditions%20to%20arms%20sales%2C%20besides%20the%20fact%20that%20its%20defence%20products%20are%20of%20high%20quality%2C%20though%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20statement%20lauds%20the%20all-round%20progress%20in%20defence%20and%20security%20partnership%2C%20which%20is%20seen%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20principal%20pillar%20of%20the%20partnership%20and%20a%20source%20of%20strengthening%20their%20countries'%20sovereignty%20and%20strategic%20autonomy%26quot%3B.%20It%20extends%20from%20intelligence%20and%20information%20exchange%20to%20exercises%20and%20equipment%20and%20across%20all%20domains%20from%20the%20seabed%20to%20space.%20Macron%20and%20Modihave%20reiterated%20their%20commitment%20to%20further%20deepening%20the%20integration%20between%20the%20two%20countries'%20respective%20defence%20industrial%20sectors%20and%20to%20work%20together%20to%20identify%20opportunities%20for%20co-design%2C%20co-development%2C%20co-production%20with%20the%20objective%20of%20not%20only%20fulfilling%20the%20defence%20needs%20of%20the%20Indian%20armed%20forces%2C%20but%20also%20of%20providing%20a%20viable%20and%20reliable%20source%20of%20defence%20supplies%20to%20other%20friendly%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETowards%20this%20end%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20welcomed%20the%20adoption%20of%20an%20ambitious%20Defence%20Industrial%20Roadmap.%20The%20exact%20content%20of%20this%20roadmap%20has%20not%20been%20divulged%2C%20but%20it%20appears%20that%20it%20opens%20the%20door%20to%20ambitious%20collaborations%20in%20sensitive%20areas.%20It%20includes%20plans%20to%20add%20MRO%20for%20Rafale%20engines%2C%20a%20comprehensive%20helicopter%20partnership%20with%20a%20Joint%20Venture%20for%20IMRH%20engine%20between%20HAL%20and%20Safran%2C%20and%20the%20Scorpene%20submarines%20constructed%20in%20India%2C%20including%20indigenisation.%20India's%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20(DRDO)%20and%20the%20French%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Armament%20(DGA)%20intend%20to%20conclude%20an%20Arrangement%20MoU%20in%20an%20early%20timeframe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20space%2C%20the%20co-development%2C%20manufacture%20and%20launch%20of%20satellites%20and%20payloads%2C%20research%20in%20new%20launch%20vehicle%20technologies%20and%20reusable%20launch%20vehicles%20and%20connecting%20the%20startups%20and%20users%20in%20both%20countries%20are%20envisaged.%20The%20MoU%20between%20NSIL%20and%20Arianespace%20is%20intended%20to%20build%20a%20long-term%20partnership%20on%20satellite%20launch%20missions.%20Modi%20and%20Macron%20have%20also%20welcomed%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20Letter%20of%20Intent%20on%20Defence%20Space%20Cooperation%2C%20which%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20very%20substantial%20military%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Jaitapur%20Nuclear%20Power%20Plant%20Project%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20very%20high%20unit%20cost%20seems%20almost%20intractable.%20The%20French%20side%20wanted%20some%20positive%20move%20towards%20implementation%20but%20India%20was%20reluctant%20to%20invest%20more%20funds%20in%20proposed%20mechanisms%20to%20that%20end.%20Eventually%2C%20as%20a%20compromise%20language%2C%20it%20has%20been%20agreed%20to%20convene%20a%20special%20task%20force%20on%20nuclear%20energy%20within%20three%20months%20in%20the%20framework%20of%20the%20Indo-French%20Strategic%20Dialogue.%20On%20the%20issue%20of%20Small%20Modular%20Reactors%20(SMRs)%20the%20potential%20for%20cooperation%20exists%20as%20India%20needs%20to%20enhance%20the%20capacity%20of%20its%20own%20indigenous%20SMRs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20expressed%20satisfaction%20with%20their%20close%20cooperation%20through%20their%20jointly%20launched%20International%20Solar%20Alliance%20to%20support%20third%20countries%20in%20their%20solar%20programmes.%20They%20welcomed%20the%20agreement%20to%20support%20creation%20of%20a%20Solar%20Academy%20in%20Senegal%20through%20joint%20research%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20of%20Airbus%20in%20partnership%20with%20Tata%20Advanced%20System%20to%20begin%20the%20assembly%20of%20civilian%20helicopters%20(H125)%20in%20India.%20They%20will%20become%20the%20first%20private%20sector%20company%20to%20produce%20helicopters%20in%20India%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20strategy%20of%20Atmanirbhar%20Bharat.%20Airbus%20is%20also%20placing%20growing%20orders%20for%20aircraft%20parts%20in%20India%20for%20its%20assembly%20plants%20in%20Europe.%20Airlines%20in%20India%20have%20placed%20huge%20orders%20for%20Airbus%20planes.%20That%20Airbus%20builds%20planes%20in%20India%20as%20the%20company%20has%20done%20in%20China%20is%20met%20with%20reservations%20by%20France%2C%20which%20has%20experienced%20China's%20technology%20theft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20meeting%20with%20select%20Indian%20business%20leaders%2C%20Macron%20pressed%20for%20Indian%20investments%20in%20France%20for%20which%20his%20government%20was%20considering%20legislation%20similar%20to%20the%20US%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act.%20Indian%20companies%20could%20invest%20in%20French%20advanced%20technology%20companies%20but%20without%20acquiring%20control.%20With%20the%20huge%20database%20in%20India%20and%20human%20talent%20available%20there%20was%20great%20scope%20of%20cooperation%20in%20AI.%20Macron%20was%20not%20fully%20aware%20of%20the%20huge%20investments%20being%20made%20in%20developing%20infrastructure%20in%20India%20and%20was%20keen%20that%20French%20companies%20participate%20in%20this%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron's%20late%20night%20visit%20to%20Dargah%20Nizamuddin%20Aulia%20before%20his%20departure%20from%20India%20was%20intended%20to%20send%20a%20message%20to%20constituencies%20back%20home%20about%20the%20Muslim%20minority%20in%20India.%20That%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20accompanied%20him%20was%20diplomatic%20on%20our%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Kanwal%20Sibal%20was%20Foreign%20Secretary%20and%20Ambassador%20to%20Turkey%2C%20Egypt%2C%20France%2C%20and%20Russia%2C%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Of%20Mission%20in%20Washington.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706519400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F3t2bipmo_pm-modi-and-macron_625x300_27_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-strong-political-message-behind-macrons-india-visit-4953013%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Emmanuel%20Macron's%20visit%20to%20India%20as%20chief%20guest%20at%20our%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations%20had%20a%20ceremonial%20aspect%2C%20no%20doubt%2C%20but%20in%20relations%20between%20states%20ceremonial%20gestures%20convey%20a%20message%20at%20many%20levels.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-strong-political-message-behind-macrons-india-visit-4953013%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-strong-political-message-behind-macrons-india-visit-4953013%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-strong-political-message-behind-macrons-india-visit-4953013%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDTV%20Explains%3A%20Why%20Was%20Hanuman%20Flag%20Taken%20Down%20In%20Karnataka's%20Mandya%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBattle%20lines%20have%20been%20drawn%20in%20Karnataka's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fmandya%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20district%20after%20officials%20last%20week%20took%20down%20a%20saffron-coloured%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fhanuman-flag-row%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHanuman%20flag%3C%2F