%20within%20striking%20distance%20of.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fschirkoa-in-lies-we-trust-review-an-animation-film-of-stunning-power-4952903%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCan't%20Just%20Board%20Any%20Train%26quot%3B%3A%20Chief%20Justice's%20Decorum%20Reminder%20To%20Lawyer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESchooling%20a%20lawyer%20on%20courtroom%20decorum%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20today%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20a%20(railway)%20platform%20where%20you%20can%20board%20any%20train%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strong%20remarks%20came%20after%20a%20lawyer%20started%20arguing%20in%20court%20out%20of%20turn.%20Around%20noon%2C%20the%20lawyer%20suddenly%20stood%20up%20and%20said%20he%20has%20submitted%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20for%20judicial%20reforms%20and%20wants%20an%20urgent%20hearing.%20The%20matter%20was%20not%20listed%20for%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20was%20livid%20at%20the%20sudden%20mention%20of%20an%20unlisted%20matter.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20platform%20that%20you%20can%20board%20any%20train.%20Speak%20to%20a%20senior%20on%20how%20to%20behave%20in%20a%20court%20and%20what%20are%20the%20rules.%20You%20are%20a%20lawyer%2C%20right%3F%20You%20should%20know%20when%20and%20how%20to%20mention%20matters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20persisted%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20is%20not%20against%20the%20judicial%20system%2C%20but%20only%20wants%20improvements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20then%20asked%20where%20he%20practises.%20The%20lawyer%20responded%20that%20he%20appears%20in%20the%20high%20court%20and%20lower%20courts.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20don't%20you%20work%20with%20a%20senior%20advocate%20who%20can%20train%20him%20in%20(courtroom)%20decorum%20and%20mannerisms%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20stickler%20for%20courtroom%20decorum%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20has%20often%20pulled%20up%20advocates%20who%20have%20crossed%20the%20etiquette%20line.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20a%20lawyer%20arguing%20at%20high%20pitch%20was%20in%20for%20a%20reprimand%20from%20the%20Chief%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20do%20you%20normally%20practice%3F%20You%20can't%20browbeat%20us%20by%20raising%20your%20voice.%20This%20has%20not%20happened%20in%20the%2023%20years%20of%20my%20career%2C%20and%20it%20will%20not%20happen%20in%20my%20last%20year.%20Lower%20your%20pitch%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20this%20the%20way%20you%20argue%20before%20the%20first%20court%20of%20the%20country%3F%20Is%20this%20how%20you%20always%20shout%20at%20judges%3F%20Lower%20your%20pitch%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20repeated.%20The%20lawyer%20eventually%20apologised%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20he%20had%20noticed%20a%20lawyer%20talking%20over%20his%20cellphone%20inside%20the%20courtroom.%20The%20Chief%20Justice%20had%20asked%20the%20lawyer%20if%20the%20court%20%26quot%3Bis%20a%20market%20where%20he%20can%20chat%20over%20the%20phone%26quot%3B%20and%20asked%20the%20court's%20staff%20to%20confiscate%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706517480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fprn22lto_chief-justice_650x400_26_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachud-chief-justices-decorum-lesson-for-lawyer-who-spoke-out-of-turn-in-court-4952707%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Schooling%20a%20lawyer%20on%20courtroom%20decorum%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20today%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20a%20(railway)%20platform%20where%20you%20can%20board%20any%20train%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachud-chief-justices-decorum-lesson-for-lawyer-who-spoke-out-of-turn-in-court-4952707%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachud-chief-justices-decorum-lesson-for-lawyer-who-spoke-out-of-turn-in-court-4952707%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachud-chief-justices-decorum-lesson-for-lawyer-who-spoke-out-of-turn-in-court-4952707%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20Says%20Citizenship%20Law%20To%20Be%20Implemented%20In%20A%20Week%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Shantanu%20Thakur%20on%20Monday%20said%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA)%20would%20be%20implemented%20in%20the%20country%20within%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20interview%20with%20a%20news%20channel%2C%20Mr%20Thakur%2C%20a%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Bongaon%2C%20an%20area%20with%20the%20majority%20of%20people%20belonging%20to%20the%20Matua%20community%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%2C%20said%20that%20swift%20implementation%20of%20the%20contentious%20legislation%20would%20be%20made%20within%20seven%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%2C%20enacted%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20in%202019%2C%20aims%20at%20granting%20Indian%20citizenship%20to%20persecuted%20non-Muslim%20migrants%2C%20including%20Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Jains%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Parsis%20and%20Christians%2C%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20Afghanistan%20who%20entered%20India%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CAA%20will%20be%20implemented%20very%20soon.%20It%20will%20be%20implemented%20within%20seven%20days.%20This%20is%20my%20guarantee%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Thakur%2C%20also%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Matua%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thakur%2C%20the%20union%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20ports%2C%20shipping%20and%20waterways%2C%20has%20made%20a%20similar%20comment%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20claiming%20that%20the%20CAA%20would%20be%20implemented%20in%20the%20country%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatuas%2C%20who%20constitute%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20the%20state's%20Scheduled%20Caste%20population%2C%20had%20been%20migrating%20to%20West%20Bengal%20since%20the%201950s%2C%20primarily%20due%20to%20religious%20persecution%20in%20erstwhile%20East%20Pakistan%20which%20later%20became%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20nineties%2C%20political%20parties%20in%20West%20Bengal%20have%20actively%20sought%20to%20secure%20the%20support%20of%20the%20Matuas%2C%20who%2C%20due%20to%20their%20significant%20population%20and%20tendency%20to%20vote%20together%2C%20are%20considered%20a%20valuable%20voting%20bloc%20akin%20to%20the%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Matua%20community%20is%20believed%20to%20benefit%20the%20most%20from%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThakur's%20assertion%20on%20the%20CAA's%20implementation%20comes%20amidst%20reports%20this%20month%2C%20suggesting%20that%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20legislation%20would%20be%20notified%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20before%26quot%3B%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20elicited%20strong%20reactions%20from%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20has%20vehemently%20opposed%20the%20CAA%2C%20labelling%20it%20%26quot%3Bdivisive%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20party%20supremo%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20have%20clearly%20said%20that%20CAA%20won't%20be%20implemented%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20attempting%20political%20gimmickry%20by%20making%20such%20false%20promises%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20TMC%20spokesperson%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20reiterated%20that%20the%20implementation%20of%20CAA%20is%20inevitable%20as%20it%20is%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20BJP%20meeting%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20he%20had%20accused%20Banerjee%20of%20misleading%20people%20on%20the%20CAA%20issue%20The%20TMC%20has%20consistently%20opposed%20the%20CAA%2C%20with%20Banerjee%20alleging%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20%26quot%3Bexploiting%26quot%3B%20the%20citizenship%20issue%20for%20political%20gain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20promise%20of%20implementing%20the%20controversial%20CAA%20served%20as%20a%20major%20electoral%20platform%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20previous%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20assembly%20polls%20in%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20leaders%20believe%20that%20it%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20the%20BJP's%20rise%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20manual%20of%20parliamentary%20procedures%2C%20the%20rules%20for%20any%20legislation%20should%20have%20been%20framed%20within%20six%20months%20of%20presidential%20assent%20or%20seek%20an%20extension%20from%20the%20committees%20on%20subordinate%20legislation%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202020%2C%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20has%20been%20taking%20extensions%20at%20regular%20intervals%20from%20the%20parliamentary%20committees%20for%20framing%20the%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706516940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F83om9o1g_shantanu-thakur_625x300_29_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-minister-shantanu-thakur-says-citizenship-law-to-be-implement-in-a-week-report-4952500%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20Shantanu%20Thakur%20on%20Monday%20said%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA)%20would%20be%20implemented%20in%20the%20country%20within%20a%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-minister-shantanu-thakur-says-citizenship-law-to-be-implement-in-a-week-report-4952500%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-minister-shantanu-thakur-says-citizenship-law-to-be-implement-in-a-week-report-4952500%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-minister-shantanu-thakur-says-citizenship-law-to-be-implement-in-a-week-report-4952500%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BParents%20Shouldn't%20Treat%20Child's%20Report%20Card%20As%20Visiting%20Card%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Monday%20said%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20instill%20resilience%20in%20children%20to%20help%20them%20cope%20with%20pressures%20and%20asserted%20that%20parents%20and%20teachers%20should%20collectively%20address%20challenges%20faced%20by%20students.%20Interacting%20with%20students%2C%20parents%20and%20teachers%20during%20his%20annual%20Pariksha%20Pe%20Charcha%20programme%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20advised%20parents%20against%20treating%20their%20child's%20report%20card%20as%20their%20own%20visiting%20card%20and%20suggested%20that%20students%20should%20compete%20with%20themselves%20and%20not%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20crucial%20to%20instill%20resilience%20in%20our%20children%20and%20help%20them%20cope%20with%20pressures...%20We%20cannot%20do%20switch%20off%2C%20pressure%20is%20gone.%20One%20must%20become%20capable%20of%20bearing%20any%20kind%20of%20pressure.%20They%20should%20believe%20that%20pressure%20keeps%20on%20building%2C%20and%20one%20has%20to%20prepare%20oneself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20also%20suggested%20students%20to%20%26quot%3Balways%20make%20friends%20who%20are%20more%20intelligent%20and%20work%20harder%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BYou%20must%20be%20inspired%20by%20such%20friends.%20Don't%20let%20the%20pressure%20of%20studies%20and%20examinations%20overpower%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20that%20even%20though%20competition%20and%20challenges%20act%20as%20inspirations%20but%20competition%20must%20be%20healthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLot%20of%20parents%20keep%20on%20giving%20examples%20of%20other%20children%20to%20their%20children.%20Parents%20should%20avoid%20doing%20these%20things...%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20also%20seen%20that%20those%20parents%20who%20have%20not%20been%20very%20successful%20in%20their%20lives%20have%20nothing%20to%20say%20or%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20world%20about%20their%20successes%20and%20achievements%2C%20make%20the%20report%20card%20of%20their%20children%20as%20their%20visiting%20card.%20Whenever%20they%20meet%20someone%2C%20they%20will%20tell%20them%20the%20story%20of%20their%20children.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BYou%20must%20not%20compare%20one%20child%20with%20another%20as%20that%20can%20be%20detrimental%20to%20their%20future.%20Some%20parents%20treat%20their%20children's%20report%20card%20as%20their%20visiting%20card%2C%20this%20is%20not%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20the%20seventh%20episode%20of%20his%20outreach%20programme%20with%20students%20ahead%20of%20examinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20explained%20that%20the%20stress%20faced%20by%20students%20is%20of%20three%20types%20--induced%20by%20peer%20pressure%2C%20by%20parents%20and%20self%20induced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20times%2C%20children%20take%20pressure%20on%20themselves%20that%20they%20are%20not%20performing%20up%20to%20the%20mark.%20I%20suggest%20that%20you%20should%20set%20small%20goals%20during%20preparation%20and%20gradually%20improve%20your%20performance%2C%20this%20way%20you%20will%20be%20completely%20ready%20before%20exams%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20make%20ourselves%20capable%20of%20facing%20any%20sort%20of%20pressure.%20Students%20need%20to%20make%20themselves%20ready%20to%20go%20through%20any%20condition.%20If%20we%20visit%20any%20cold%20place%2C%20we%20make%20up%20our%20minds%2C%20and%20accordingly%2C%20we%20keep%20ourselves%20ready...(in%20the)%20same%20way%20you%20have%20to%20be%20ready%20for%20exams%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20said%20that%20challenges%20of%20students%20must%20be%20addressed%20collectively%20by%20parents%20and%20teachers.%20He%20also%20encouraged%20teachers%20to%20forge%20strong%20connections%20with%20their%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bond%20between%20educators%20and%20learners%20is%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20bright%20future.%20If%20teachers%20start%20working%20on%20building%20a%20relationship%20with%20their%20students%20from%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20year%2C%20there%20won't%20be%20any%20question%20of%20tension%20building%20up%20among%20students%20at%20the%20time%20of%20examinations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTeachers%20must%20expand%20their%20connections%20with%20students%20much%20beyond%20their%20subject%20syllabus%20so%20that%20students%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20their%20teachers%20even%20for%20the%20smallest%20of%20problems.%20Music%20teachers%20can%20not%20only%20help%20their%20own%20students%20deal%20with%20tensions%2C%20they%20can%20do%20so%20for%20students%20of%20the%20entire%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20questions%20on%20balancing%20studies%20with%20a%20healthy%20life%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said%20many%20students%20use%20mobile-phones%20and%20some%20do%20it%20for%20many%20hours.%20He%20advised%20students%20not%20to%20use%20their%20sleep%20time%20for%20watching%20reels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20should%20understand%20that%20even%20mobiles%20need%20recharge%20to%20be%20used%2C%20and%20similarly%2C%20our%20body%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20recharged.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20some%20students%20keep%20playing%20all%20the%20time%2C%20but%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20strike%20a%20balance.%20A%20healthy%20body%20is%20necessary%20for%20a%20healthy%20mind.%20Good%20and%20sound%20sleep%20is%20also%20a%20must%20for%20good%20health.%20Don't%20use%20your%20sleep%20time%20for%20watching%20reels%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20get%20into%20deep%20sleep%20within%2030%20seconds%20of%20lying%20on%20the%20bed%20on%20all%20365%20days.%20When%20I%20am%20awake%2C%20I%20am%20fully%20awake%2C%20but%20I%20am%20totally%20asleep%20while%20sleeping.%20Nutrition%20is%20also%20necessary.%20Our%20body%20must%20get%20the%20required%20nutrition.%20A%20good%20balance%20of%20food%20and%20regular%20exercise%20for%20fitness%20are%20also%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20also%20advised%20students%20to%20practice%20writing.%20%26quot%3BIn%20this%20age%20of%20mobile%20phones%20and%20laptops%2C%20students%20are%20losing%20the%20practice%20to%20write%20while%20exams%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20handwritten.%20Of%20the%20time%20dedicated%20to%20studies%2C%20you%20should%20devote%20at%20least%2050%20per%20cent%20time%20to%20practise%20writing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20students%20as%20the%20shapers%20of%20India's%20future%2C%20Modi%20said%20the%20Pariksha%20Pe%20Charcha%20programme%20is%20like%20an%20examination%20for%20him%20too.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20students%20have%20become%20more%20innovative%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrganised%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20Pariksha%20P