0a%20local%20profanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20if%20Kohli%20knew%20the%20meaning%20of%20the%20word%2C%20Elgar%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20he%20did%20because%20de%20Villiers%20was%20his%20teammate%20at%20RCB%2C%20so%20he%20understood.%20And%20I%20said%20if%20you%20do%20that%2C%20I'll%20...%20on%20this%20field%2C%20I'll%20absolutely%20knock%20you%20out.%20And%20then%20%5Bhe%20said%5D%20'Hey%20F***%20you%2C%20F***%20you'%20(mimicking%20the%20Indian)%20but%20barking%20up%20the%20wrong%20tree%20yeah.%20Anyways%2C%20we%20are%20in%20India%20so%20you%20got%20to%20be%20a%20little%20bit%20cautious.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElgar%2C%20however%2C%20revealed%20that%20Kohli%20apologised%20to%20him%20for%20his%20behaviour%20over%20a%20few%20drinks%20when%20India%20toured%20South%20Africa%20in%202017-18.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo%20three%20years%20later%2C%20Kohli%20pulled%20me%20aside%20and%20said%20'listen%2C%20can%20we%20go%20and%20have%20a%20drink%20after%20the%20series%20i%20want%20to%20apologise%20for%20my%20actions'.%20So%20we%20drank%20till%203%20in%20the%20morning.%20This%20is%20when%20he%20used%20to%20drink%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElgar%20played%20his%20last%20Test%20against%20India%20earlier%20this%20month%20at%20the%20Newlands%20in%20Cape%20Town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20final%20Test%2C%20Elgar%20captained%20South%20Africa%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Temba%20Bavuma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1540-temba-bavuma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ETemba%20Bavuma%3C%2Fa%3E%20missing%20out%20due%20to%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20India%20won%20the%20second%20Test%20to%20level%20the%20series%201-1.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706515140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F3valpigo_dean-elgar-virat-kohli_625x300_29_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fvirat-kohli-spat-at-me-i-said-south-