D%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Nitish%20resigned%20from%20his%20post%20as%20chief%20minister%20after%20exiting%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20rejoining%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20only%20to%20be%20sworn%20in%20again%20for%20the%20ninth%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706508014000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F29112459%2FPK-NK.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnitishs-flip-shows-modi-shah-too-can-vie-for-palturam-moniker-prashant-kishor%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20added%20that%20Nitish's%20party%20will%20not%20win%20more%20than%2020%20seats%20in%20the%20next%20assembly%20elections%2C%20no%20matter%20who%20it%20is%20in%20alliance%20with.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnitishs-flip-shows-modi-shah-too-can-vie-for-palturam-moniker-prashant-kishor%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suspended%20WFI%20Holds%20its%20Own%20'Nationals'%2C%20Leading%20to%20a%20Quandary%20for%20India's%20Wrestlers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21155114%2FEffect-38.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20community%20continues%20to%20face%20chaos%20and%20administrative%20confusion%2C%20as%20the%20suspended%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%2C%20with%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20loyalist%20Sanjay%20Singh%20at%20its%20helm%2C%20hold%20%E2%80%98senior%20nationals%E2%80%99%20in%20Pune%20despite%20its%20suspension.%20Most%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20players%2C%20however%2C%20are%20giving%20this%20tournament%20a%20miss%20and%20instead%20attending%20the%20%E2%80%98nationals%E2%80%99%20organised%20by%20the%20ad%20hoc%20committee%20set%20up%