%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fsuspended-wfi-holds-its-own-nationals-leading-to-a-quandary-for-indias-wrestlers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Most%20of%20India's%20top%20players%20are%20giving%20this%20tournament%20a%20miss%20and%20instead%20attending%20the%20'nationals'%20organised%20by%20the%20ad%20hoc%20committee%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Union%20sports%20minister%20early%20next%20month%2C%20in%20Jaipur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fsuspended-wfi-holds-its-own-nationals-leading-to-a-quandary-for-indias-wrestlers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20SC%20Diamond%20Jubilee%20Event%2C%20PM%20Modi's%20'Central%20Vista%20Petitions'%20Reference%2C%20Ram%20and%20'Inherent%20Bias'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F29103301%2FScreenshot-2024-01-29-at-10.32.53%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20At%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20diamond%20jubilee%20year%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20appeared%20to%20deliver%20a%20slight%20to%20critics%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcentral-vista-redevelopment-national-museum-archives-heritage%5C%22%3ERs%2013%2C000-crore%20Central%20Vista%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20noting%20that%20he%20hoped%20that%20no%20petitions%20would%20be%20filed%20challenging%20the%20Union%20government%20allocating%20crores%20over%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20given%20our%20approval%20of%20Rs%20800%20crores%20%5Bin%20the%20latest%20tranche%5D%20for%20the%20expansion%20of%20Supreme%20Court%20building.%20Now%20just%20hope%20that%20no%20one%20comes%20with%20a%20petition%20stating%20that%20it%20is%20useless%20spending%20like%20what%20happened%20during%20the%20Central%20Vista%20construction%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20PM%20said%2C%20according%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2F800-crores-approved-new-supreme-court-building-prime-minister-narendra-modi%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Bar%20and%20Bench.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20added%20that%20since%202014%2C%20when%20he%20came%20to%20power%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20allocated%20over%20Rs%207%2C000%20crore%20for%20the%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20also%20said%20that%20the%20rule%20of%20the%20Hindu%20deity%20Ram%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Csource%20of%20inspiration%20for%20the%20constitution%20makers%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI.%20He%20said%20pictures%20of%20Ram%2C%20Sita%20and%20Lakshman%20%E2%80%93%20who%20feature%20in%20the%20epic%20%3Cem%3ERamayan%3C%2Fem%3E%20adorned%20the%20pages%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Modi%20inaugurated%20the%20Ram%20temple%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20which%20was%20constructed%20after%20a%202019%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Hindu%20litigants%20in%20the%20dispute%20over%20the%20title.%20The%20temple%20stands%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20%E2%80%93%20demolished%20by%20kar%20sevaks%20in%201992%20%E2%80%93%20once%20stood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modi-addresses-75th-anniversary-celebrations-of-the-supreme-court-in-new-delhi%2Farticle67785757.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20notes%20that%20Modi%20also%20complimented%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20for%20his%20efforts%20to%20improve%20ease%20of%20justice%20in%20the%20country.%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20bench%20that%20delivered%20the%20aforementioned%202019%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20also%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20using%20technology%20for%20ease%20of%20justice%2C%20which%20he%20also%20stressed%20as%20the%20right%20of%20every%20Indian%20citizen.%20He%20called%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20its%20medium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECJI%20Chandrachud%20chaired%20the%20ceremonial%20bench%20with%20all%20apex%20court%20judges%20and%20the%20Chief%20Justices%20of%2025%20high%20courts%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Findependence-of-judiciary-depends-on-the-freedom-of-every-individual-judge-to-decide-without-pressure-or-bias-cji%2Farticle67786330.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%20noted%20that%20he%20said%20that%20an%20independent%20judiciary%20does%20not%20%E2%80%9Cmerely%20mean%20the%20insulation%20of%20the%20institution%20from%20the%20executive%20and%20the%20legislature%20branches%20but%20also%20the%20independence%20of%20individual%20judges%20in%20the%20performance%20of%20their%20roles%20as%20judges.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20art%20of%20judging%20must%20be%20free%20of%20social%20and%20political%20pressure%20and%20from%20the%20inherent%20biases%20which%20human%20beings%20hold%2C%E2%80%9D%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20efforts%20had%20been%20undertaken%20to%20train%20judges%20to%20%E2%80%9Cunlearn%20their%20subconscious%20attitudes%20inculcated%20by%20social%20conditioning%20on%20gender%2C%20disability%2C%20race%2C%20caste%20and%20sexuality%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20has%20been%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fkaran-thapar-justice-chandrachud-cji-dushyant-dave%5C%22%3Ereceiving%20end%20of%20criticism%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20fact%20that%20recent%20judgments%20and%20allocation%20of%20cases%20reflect%20a%20stance%20of%20the%20court%20to%20not%20displease%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706504717000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F29103301%2FScreenshot-2024-01-29-at-10.32.53%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-diamond-jubilee-narendra-modi-central-vista-chandrachud%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20PM%20also%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20using%20technology%20for%20ease%20of%20justice%2C%20which%20he%20also%20noted%20was%20the%20right%20of%20every%20Indian%20citizen.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-diamond-jubilee-narendra-modi-central-vista-chandrachud%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Convictions%2C%20'No%20Support%20From%20Activists'%20as%20Sharjeel%20Imam%20Spends%20Four%20Years%20in%20Jail%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F24192815%2FUntitled-design-2021-10-24T192755.811.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJanuary%2028%2C%202024%2C%20marks%20four%20years%20in%20jail%20for%20Sharjeel%20Imam%2C%20IIT-graduate-turned-PhD-scholar%20at%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImam%20was%20arrested%20in%202020%20after%20police%20in%20five%20different%20states%20%E2%80%93%20Assam%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Manipur%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%93%20filed%20first%20information%20reports%20against%20him%20in%20connection%20with%20speeches%20he%20made%20during%20the%20protests%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20and%20the%20National%20Register%20for%20Citizens%20(NRC).%20Among%20other%20charges%2C%20he%20was%20charged%20under%20sedition%20and%20subsequently%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%20(UAPA)%20and%20also%20named%20as%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20Delhi%20riots%20%E2%80%9Clarger%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20case.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImam%20has%20spent%20four%20years%20in%20jail%2C%20despite%20not%20being%20convicted%20in%20any%20of%20the%20cases.%20Of%20the%20total%20eight%20cases%20against%20him%2C%20he%20has%20been%20given%20bail%20in%20five%2C%20never%20been%20arrested%20in%20one%2C%20and%20has%20only%20the%20UAPA%20cases%20against%20him%20remaining.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20four%20years%20have%20also%20seen%20his%20bail%20petitions%20pending%20in%20various%20Delhi%20courts%2C%20including%20one%20petition%20filed%20last%20year%20in%20which%20he%20has%20sought%20immediate%20bail%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20he%20has%20completed%20more%20than%20half%20the%20maximum%20punishment%20(seven%20years)%20under%20Section%2013%20of%20UAPA.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFour%20years%20of%20his%20life%20have%20been%20wasted.%20If%20he%20was%20out%2C%20he%20could%20have%20studied%20more%2C%20he%20could%20have%20researched%20more.%20He%20is%20yet%20to%20complete%20his%20PhD.%20But%20his%20morale%20is%20not%20low.%20He%20keeps%20smiling%20and%20gives%20our%20mother%20hope%20as%20well%20saying%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Ammi%2C%20sab%20thik%20ho%20jayega%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(Mother%2C%20everything%20will%20be%20alright)%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20younger%20brother%20Muzammil%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20any%20political%20prisoner%20who%20is%20in%20jail%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20stability%20is%20lost%20for%20their%20family.%20For%20my%20mother%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20the%20two%20of%20us.%20In%20a%20way%20life%20has%20come%20to%20a%20standstill%20since%20that%20sense%20of%20stability%20is%20lost.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFour%20years%20since%20he%20was%20arrested%2C%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20has%20listed%20Imam%E2%80%99s%20bail%20plea%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdelayed-justice-alleged-violation-constitutional-rights-quest-bail-delhi-riots-accused%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E46%20times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20is%20now%20set%20to%20hear%20his%20plea%20afresh%20next%20month%20in%20connection%20to%20the%20Delhi%20riots%20case%20under%20FIR%2059%2F2020.%20His%20bail%20plea%20under%20the%20first%20FIR%2020%2F2020%20under%20which%20he%20was%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20his%20speeches%2C%20will%20also%20begin%20afresh%20next%20month%20in%20a%20lower%20court%20in%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuzammil%20said%20that%20when%20Imam%20went%20to%20jail%2C%20the%20family%20knew%20that%20it%20would%20probably%20take%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20for%20him%20to%20get%20bail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20did%20not%20think%20it%20would%20go%20on%20for%20so%20many%20years.%20After%20his%20arrest%2C%20the%20north%20east%20Delhi%20riots%20took%20place.%20Yet%20he%20was%20implicated%20in%20that%20for%20no%20reason%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Muzammil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsharjeel-imam-speech%5C%22%3EWhat%20Sharjeel%20Imam%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Seditious%E2%80%99%20Speech%20Has%20in%20Common%20with%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJudicial%20delays%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20his%20counsel%20Ahmad%20Ibrahim%2C%20Imam%20was%20arrested%20on%20January%2028%2C%202020%20just%20days%20after%20his%20speech%20at%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20during%20the%20CAA-NRC%20protest%20in%20which%20he%20asked%20for%20Assam%20to%20be%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsedition-case-jnu-student-sharjeel-imam%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Ccut%20off%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Efrom%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20speech%20is%20dated%20January%2016%20but%20went%20viral%20on%20January%2025%2C%202020.%20By%20January%2026%2C%202020%20there%20were%20five%20FIRs%20registered%20against%20him%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Assam%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Manipur.%20Two%20days%20later%20on%20January%2028%2C%20he%20was%20arrested%20by%20Delhi%20police%20when%20he%20was%20going%20to%20surrender%20along%20with%20his%20counsel%20in%20connection%20to%20the%20Delhi%20FIR.%20Some%20months%20later%20when%20the%20Delhi%20riots%20case%20was%20registered%20he%20was%20named%20in%20the%20supplementary%20chargesheet%20with%20Umar%20Khalid%20in%20the%20FIR%2059%2F2020.%20He%20was%20also%20made%20an%20accused%20in%20two%20more%20cases-which%20relate%20to%20the%20violence%20near%20Jamia%20Milia%20University%20in%20December%202019.%20Of%20the%20total%20eight%20cases%20against%20him%2C%20he%20has%20got%20bail%20in%20five%2C%20never%20arrested%20in%20one%20and%20only%20the%20UAPA%20cases%20against%20him%20remain%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ibrahim%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20he%20has%20been%20charged%20under%20Section%2013%20of%20the%20UAPA%20in%20FIR%2022%2F2020%2C%20he%20faces%20multiple%20charges%20under%20the%20UAPA%20in%20FIR%2059%2F2020%20which%20relates%20to%20the%20Delhi%20riots%20%E2%80%9Clarger%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20case.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20August%20last%20year%2C%20Imam%20moved%20court%20seeking%20immediate%20bail%20under%20Section%20436A%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(CRPC)%20in%20connection%20with%20FIR%2022%2F2020%20in%20which%20he%20has%20been%20charged%20under%20Section%2013%20of%20the%20UAPA%20along%20with%20124A%20(sedition)%20and%20153A%2C%20153B%2C%20505%20of%20IPC.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20bail%20application%2C%20he%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Estated%20that%20the%20sedition%20proceedings%20had%20been%20stayed%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20in%202022%20put%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffull-text-what-the-supreme-court-said-while-putting-the-sedition-law-on-hold%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehold%20on%20the%20sedition%20law.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20application%20states%20that%20bail%20is%20sought%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20%E2%80%9Che%20had%20completed%20a%20period%20of%203%20years%20and%20more%20than%206%20months%20under%20incarceration%20and%20has%20undergone%20incarceration%20extending%20up%20to%20one-half%20of%20the%20maximum%20period%20of%20imprisonment%20specified%20for%20the%20concerned%20offence%20by%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsharjeel-imam-discharged-2019-jamia-violence-case%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Scapegoats%E2%80%99%3A%20Delhi%20Court%20Discharges%20Sharjeel%20Imam%2C%2010%20Others%20From%202019%20Jamia%20Violence%20Case%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImam%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20Ibrahim%20said%20that%20his%20bail%20plea%20under%20Section%20436A%20has%20been%20pending%20for%20over%20four%20months%20as%20the%20judgement%20was%20not%20passed%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%2C%20including%20the%20transfer%20of%20the%20presiding%20judge%20Amitabh%20Rawat%20whose%20transfer%20was%20announced%20in%20December%20and%20said%20in%20the%20last%20date%20of%20hearing%20that%20the%20next%20judge%20will%20hear%20the%20matter%20afresh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20though%20it%20is%20statutory%20bail%2C%20as%20he%20has%20completed%20half%20the%20maximum%20punishment%2C%20still%20he%20has%20not%20been%20given%20bail.%20Now%20on%20February%207%20the%20matter%20has%20been%20listed%20in%20front%20of%20another%20judge%20who%20will%20consider%20the%20matter%20afresh%20and%20then%20pass%20an%20order%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ibrahim.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20bail%20under%20FIR%2059%2F2020%20is%20pending%20before%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20for%20twenty%20months%20now%20and%20has%20been%20listed%20for%20hearing%20on%20February%2022.%20His%20regular%20bail%20under%20FIR%2022%2F2020%20is%20also%20pending%20before%20high%20court%20but%20when%20he%20completed%20half%20the%20punishment%20we%20requested%20the%20court%20that%20let%20me%20get%20released%20on%20interim%20bail%20under%20Section%20436A%20but%20that%20also%20was%20not%20granted%20and%20were%20asked%20to%20approach%20the%20trial%20court.%20So%20we%20approached%20the%20lower%20court%20where%20again%20the%20matter%20was%20kept%20pending%20for%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20hopeful%20somewhere%20some%20judge%20will%20pass%20the%20order%20where%20bail%20is%20a%20mandatory%20provision%20under%20Section%20436A%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Delhi-based%20advocate%20Sarim%20Naved%2C%20delays%20in%20deciding%20bail%20petitions%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctragedy%E2%80%9D%20that%20goes%20against%20criminal%20jurisprudence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20tragedy%2C%20no%20bail%20application%20should%20be%20pending%20for%20two%20years.%20If%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20the%20person%20is%20suited%20for%20bail%20then%20please%20dismiss%20it%20so%20the%20person%20can%20try%20their%20luck%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20or%20a%20higher%20court.%20But%20keeping%20a%20bail%20application%20pending%20for%20two%20years%20is%20contrary%20to%20all%20expectations%20from%20criminal%20jurisprudence%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fin-prison-for-sedition-sharjeel-imam-explains-his-idea-of-india%5C%22%3EIn%20Prison%20for%20%E2%80%98Sedition%E2%80%99%2C%20Sharjeel%20Imam%20Explains%20His%20Idea%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Delay%20thanks%20to%20directions%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuzammil%20said%20that%20the%20delays%20show%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cjudiciary%20is%20working%20under%20government%20pressure%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20delay%20is%20on%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20government.%20The%20judicial%20system%20is%20working%20under%20the%20pressure%20of%20the%20government.%20This%20is%20not%20happening%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20India.%20This%20used%20to%20happen%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20power%20at%20the%20centre%20as%20well%20and%20now%20it%20is%20happening%20under%20the%20BJP.%20His%20(Sharjeel%20Imam%E2%80%99s)%20bail%20hearing%20has%20been%20postponed%2046%20times%20across%20two%20years%20in%20the%20Delhi%20riots%20cases%2C%20this%20clearly%20shows%20that%20this%20is%20political%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuzammil%20said%20that%20unlike%20other%20political%20prisoners%2C%20like%20Khalid%2C%20Imam%20has%20not%20received%20support%20from%20civil%20society%20groups%20and%20prominent%20political%20activists.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20choose%20people%20who%20they%20want%20to%20support%20and%20who%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSharjeel%20has%20been%20absent%20from%20posters%20of%20all%20leading%20organisations.%20I%20am%20not%20generalising%20but%20the%20general%20approach%20in%20all%20organisations%20is%20that%20they%20want%20to%20victimise%20the%20person%20who%20is%20behind%20bars.%20My%20brother%20is%20not%20a%20victim.%20He%20is%20a%20fighter%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20victimise%20him.%20We%20are%20not%20extraordinary.%20But%20we%20want%20to%20fight%20back%20on%20facts.%20Sharjeel%E2%80%99s%20way%20of%20talking%2C%20his%20speeches%20have%20always%20been%20different.%20Umar%20Khalid%20has%20a%20lobby%20behind%20him.%20But%20Sharjeel%20was%20just%20a%20person%20who%20nobody%20knew%20before%20CAA-NRC.%20He%20was%20just%20a%20person%20who%20was%20doing%20his%20PhD%20from%20JNU.%20He%20had%20no%20lobby%20behind%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20jail%2C%20Muzammil%20said%20Imam%20has%20been%20reading%20legal%20books%20to%20study%20the%20law%20and%20has%20also%20taken%20to%20helping%20other%20underprivileged%20undertrials%20in%20helping%20them%20get%20legal%20aid%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20access%20to%20legal%20recourse.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20no%20option%20but%20to%20keep%20hope%20that%20someday%20he%20will%20come%20out.%20It%E2%80%99s%20just%20that%20someone%E2%80%99s%20life%E2%80%99s%20precious%20years%20are%20getting%20wasted.%20They%20can%20keep%20postponing%20his%20bail%20but%20how%20long%20will%20they%20keep%20him%20in%20jail%3F%20As%20the%20saying%20goes%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%98Har%20urooj%20ka%20zawal%20dekhna%20hota%20hai%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(every%20rise%20has%20a%20fall).%E2%80%99%20This%20will%20be%20true%20for%20us%20as%20well%20as%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706500644000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F24192815%2FUntitled-design-2021-10-24T192755.811.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsharjeel-imam-jail-uapa-activist-civil-society-support%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20IIT-graduate-turned-JNU-scholar's%20brother%20Muzammil%20Imam%20said%20to%20The%20Wire%20that%20Sharjeel%20has%20not%20received%20support%20from%20civil%20society%20groups%20and%20prominent%20political%20activists.%20'They%20choose%20people%20who%20they%20want%20to%20support%20and%20who%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20support.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A129%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsharjeel-imam-jail-uapa-activist-civil-society-support%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Keeping%20Post%20Vacant%20For%2015%20Months%2C%20China%20May%20Appoint%20New%20Envoy%20to%20India%20Soon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28214931%2FIndia-and-China.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20China%20may%20finally%20have%20a%20new%20ambassador%20in%20India%20early%20this%20year%2C%20with%20Beijing%20reportedly%20having%20selected%20a%20two-time%20envoy%20to%20fill%20the%20post%2C%20which%20has%20been%20lying%20vacant%20for%20over%2015%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20learnt%20that%20China%20has%20finalised%20one%20of%20its%20assistant%20foreign%20ministers%20posted%20at%20headquarters%20in%20Beijing%2C%20Xu%20Feihong%2C%20as%20the%20next%20ambassador%20to%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%2C%20however%2C%20no%20official%20confirmation%20from%20either%20the%20Chinese%20embassy%20or%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EXu%20is%20currently%20assistant%20minister%20for%20financial%20and%20administrative%20affairs%20in%20the%20foreign%20ministry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20side%20has%20been%20conveyed%20about%20the%20candidate%2C%20as%20per%20informed%20sources.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20it%20was%20earlier%20expected%20that%20he%20could%20be%20arriving%20as%20early%20as%20around%20the%20time%20of%20the%20Spring%20Festival%20next%20month%2C%20it%20is%20uncertain%20if%20that%20timeline%20is%20feasible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EXu%E2%80%99s%20position%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mfa.gov.cn%2Fweb%2Fziliao_674904%2Fwjrw_674925%2F202102%2Ft20210218_9881048.shtml%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eassistant%20foreign%20minister%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20roughly%20equivalent%20to%20the%20rank%20of%20additional%20secretary%20in%20the%20MEA.%20Since%20the%20post%20of%20Chinese%20ambassador%20to%20India%20is%20of%20the%20vice-minister%20rank%2C%20he%20would%20need%20to%20be%20promoted%20before%20he%20comes%20to%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20previous%20two%20Chinese%20ambassadors%20to%20India%2C%20Sun%20Weidong%20and%20his%20predecessor%2C%20Lui%20Zhaohui%2C%20had%20significant%20experience%20in%20South%20Asia%2C%20including%20prior%20postings%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Lu%20Yucheng%2C%20who%20preceded%20Lui%2C%20did%20not%20have%20any%20regional%20experience.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%2037%20years%20as%20a%20Chinese%20diplomat%2C%20Xu%E2%80%99s%20only%20assignment%20in%20South%20Asia%20was%20as%20ambassador%20to%20Afghanistan%20from%202010%20to%202013.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20of%20his%20postings%20have%20been%20in%20the%20Western%20world%2C%20ranging%20from%20Finland%20to%20Australia%2C%20with%20a%20specialisation%20in%20Europe.%20His%20last%20ambassadorial%20posting%20had%20been%20in%20Romania%20from%202015%20to%202018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChina%E2%80%99s%20latest%20ambassador%20to%20India%2C%20Sun%20Weidong%2C%20left%20his%20post%20in%20October%202022%20after%20three%20years%20that%20saw%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20Asian%20neighbours%20plummet%20following%20fatal%20clashes%20in%20the%20mountainous%20heights%20of%20eastern%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20April-May%202020%2C%20India%20and%20China%20have%20been%20locked%20in%20a%20military%20stand-off%20in%20the%20western%20part%20of%20their%20long%20border.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20claimed%20that%20Chinese%20troops%20had%20moved%20further%20beyond%20their%20traditional%20positions%20on%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%2C%20resulting%20in%20multiple%20skirmishes%20with%20the%20patrolling%20teams%20of%20the%20Indian%20army.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20deadliest%20conflict%20took%20place%20on%20June%2015%2C%20when%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20troops%20engaged%20in%20a%20hand-to-hand%20fight%20at%20the%20Galwan%20valley%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%2020%20Indian%20soldiers%20and%20at%20least%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fchina-acknowledges-casualties-galwan-clash-india-army%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efour%20Chinese%20troops%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20then%2C%20at%20least%2020%20rounds%20of%20military-level%20talks%20and%2013%20rounds%20of%20foreign%20office-led%20discussions%20have%20been%20held%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20had%20led%20to%20disengagement%20at%20five%20friction%20points%20at%20the%20Pangong%20Tso%20lake%E2%80%99s%20north%20and%20south%20banks%2C%20patrolling%20points%2015%20and%2017A%20at%20the%20Gogra-Hot%20Springs%20area%20and%20Galwan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20ambassador%20Sun%20left%20in%202022%2C%20Demchok%20and%20Depsang%20were%20the%20remaining%20areas%20of%20stand-off.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFifteen%20months%20on%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20change%20on%20this%20front.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20maintains%20that%20the%20standoff%20will%20only%20be%20resolved%20once%20there%20is%20disengagement%20and%20de-escalation%20at%20Demchok%20and%20Depsang.%20In%20contrast%2C%20China%20asserts%20that%20the%20alteration%20in%20status%20quo%20after%20May%202020%20does%20not%20encompass%20these%20two%20areas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChina%20has%20repeatedly%20called%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnormalisation%E2%80%9D%20of%20ties%20and%20to%20go%20beyond%20the%20border%20dispute%2C%20but%20India%20insists%20that%20the%20stand-off%20has%20to%20be%20resolved%20first.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObservers%20interpret%20the%20prolonged%20delay%20in%20appointing%20another%20Chinese%20envoy%20to%20the%20Indian%20capital%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20holds%20a%20senior%20rank%20and%20would%20have%20enough%20takers%2C%20as%20a%20deliberate%20signal%20of%20displeasure%20from%20Beijing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20border%20issue%2C%20there%20had%20been%20other%20issues%20over%20which%20Beijing%20has%20expressed%20its%20annoyance%2C%20like%20the%20financial%20investigations%20of%20major%20Chinese%20companies%20in%20India.%20China%20had%20also%20not%20been%20happy%20when%20India%20had%20turned%20the%20SCO%20summit%20into%20a%20virtual%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20president%20Xi%20Jinping%20also%20skipped%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20India%2C%20despite%20having%20gone%20to%20Indonesia%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%201962%20war%2C%20both%20countries%20exchanged%20ambassadors%20only%20after%20a%20gap%20of%2015%20years%20in%201976.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20then%2C%20there%20has%20usually%20been%20only%20a%20short%20gap%20of%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20at%20the%20most%20between%20ambassadors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706459298000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28214931%2FIndia-and-China.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fchina-may-appoint-new-ambassador-to-india-soon%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Wire%20has%20learnt%20that%20China%20has%20finalised%20one%20of%20its%20assistant%20foreign%20ministers%20posted%20at%20headquarters%20in%20Beijing%2C%20Xu%20Feihong%2C%20as%20the%20next%20ambassador%20to%20India.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fchina-may-appoint-new-ambassador-to-india-soon%22%2C%22cdnA