2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gunfight%20continued%20until%207%3A30%20am%20and%20the%20situation%20worsened%20in%20the%20Imphal%20East%20district%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20wrote%20to%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20regarding%20the%20alleged%20assault%20on%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Congress%20president%2C%20Keisham%20Meghachandra%2C%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Arambai%20Tenggol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F7LhsAvBhLP8%3Fsi%3Ds5B5UzTMRWsRg86J%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20four-point%20letter%20to%20Shah%2C%20Kharge%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20shocking%20incident%20has%20occurred%20despite%20the%20heavy%20presence%20of%20Central%20and%20Security%20forces%2C%20and%20intelligence%20personnel.%20Till%20date%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20action%20from%20the%20Manipur%20CM%20and%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20on%20this%20disturbing%20subversion%20of%20democratic%20processes%20by%20a%20non-state%20actor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20shameful%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20eloquent%20silence%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Manipur%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20prevailing%20strategy%20from%20all%20important%20stakeholders%20in%20both%20the%20State%20and%20the%20Centre.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoreh%20continues%20to%20boil%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20border%20town%20of%20Moreh%20continues%20to%20boil%20nearly%20a%20month%20after%20security%20personnel%20there%20were%20ambushed%20by%20suspected%20militants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20number%20of%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20in%20the%20border%20town%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatodayne.in%2Fmanipur%2Fstory%2Fmanipur-kuki-zos-hold-major-sit-in-protest-demandin